(57, 14, 'BUTTER LIPSTICK', 'NYX', 'CHICCAGP-1464661299-7185.png', '<p>Hydrate your lips with this moisturizing combination of full coverage lipstick and creamy chapstick in one! Not only will you be rocking a gorgeous pout, this lipstick is designed to keep your lips feeling smooth and moisturized all day long. Plus, it smells &amp; feels like butter.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hydrating</li>\r\n	<li>Full coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Creamy satin finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.3 oz</p>\r\n', '8.5g', '<p><strong><span style="font-size:13pt">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family:roboto">candelilla wax, bees wax, carnauba wax, capric/caprylic triglyceride, tridecyl trimellitate, olive oil, 2-ethyihexyl palmitate, sunchemical, tocopherol, propylparaben. may contain: red6 (c115850), red7 (c115850:1), red27 (c116035:1), yellow5 (c119140:1), titanium dioxide (c177891), iron oxide black (c177499), blue1 (c142090:2), iron oxide yellow (c177492)</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:25:57', '03-NYX-1569-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 73, 1000, '黄油口红', 'NYX', '<p>唇膏和口红二合一带给你全天候滋润水嫩的双唇。此款口红外观是丝绒感，一触丝滑，含有黄油保温精华，轻盈顺滑不干燥，涂抹之后令双唇倍感亮泽饱满。此外，闻起来和使用时有黄油的香味。</p><ul>	<li>滋润</li>	<li>显色</li>	<li>奶油嗅感及触感</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>8.5克</p>', '<p><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">烛树蜡，蜂蜡，巴西棕榈蜡，癸酸</span><span style="font-family:roboto">/</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">辛酸甘油三酯，十三烷基偏苯三酸酯，橄榄油，棕榈酸辛酯，</span><span style="font-family:roboto">sunchemical</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">，生育酚，对羟基苯甲酸丙酯。可以含有：红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">6</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c115850</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">7</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c115850</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">27</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c116035</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），黄</span><span style="font-family:roboto">5</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c119140</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），二氧化钛（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177891</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），氧化铁黑（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177499</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），蓝</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c142090</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">2</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），铁氧化铁黄（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177492</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">）</span><span style="font-family:roboto">...)</span></p>'),
(58, 14, 'CONCEALER BRUSH', 'BEAUTIFUL PARIS', 'CHICCAGP-1461720467-89189.png', '<p><strong>DESCRIPTION</strong>&nbsp;This concealer brush is perfect for applying liquids and creams for a smoother, more flawless concealer application. It&rsquo;s also ideal for covering scars and imperfections as well as meticulously camouflaging dark circles. It comes with a handcrafted brush that enables beautiful and easy makeup applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Very thin tapered tip ensures accurate application and seamless results</li>\r\n	<li>Firm yet soft synthetic fibers bundled closely together</li>\r\n	<li>Eco friendly matt black wooden handles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.3 oz</p>\r\n', '8.5g', '<p>synthetic fibers, wooden handles</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:27:48', '19-BEAUCONC-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 70, 1000, '抗菌遮瑕刷', 'BEAUTIFUL PARIS', '<p>这款遮瑕刷可用于液体性化妆品和面霜，有助于帮你化出精致无瑕的妆容。它不仅能够用于遮盖脸部斑点瑕疵，还可用于打造精致迷彩妆。一支简单的遮瑕刷能够带给你更加完美的妆容体验。</p><ul>	<li>尖细的锥形刷头使用起来更加便捷使得妆容也更为精致。</li>	<li>合成纤维刷毛柔软且牢固不掉毛</li>	<li>生态环保亚光木柄</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>8.5克</p>', '<p>合成纤维、木制手柄</p>'),
(59, 14, 'DOUBLE BAKED FACE BLUSH', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', 'CHICCAGP-1464591707-27929.jpg', '<p>A fresh blush of brush-on sunshine without the UV damage. Sheer and buildable highlighter powder complements every skin tone, adds just enough of a natural summery glow and a glimpse of shimmer. Great when you&rsquo;re feeling a bit tired, or just longing for the beach!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.12 oz</p>\r\n', '3.4g', '<p><span style="color:black; font-family:roboto">talc, mica, magnesium stearate, stearic acid, ethylhexyl palmitate, paraffinum liquidum, polybutene, microcrystalline wax, bees wax, dimethicone</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:black; font-family:roboto">may contain (+/-): red iron oxide ci 77491, titaninium dioxide ci 77891, black iron oxide ci 77499, brown iron oxide ci 77491/92/99, red no 6 ba ci 15850</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:31:38', '03-MEADIFF-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 71, 1000, '粉红色和玫瑰粉色双色腮红', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', '<p>这款清新自然色彩柔和的腮红让你远离紫外线的伤害。荧光粉有助力于提亮肤色，自然通透感与鲜活粉嫩结合得恰到好处。在你感到一丝丝疲惫或者想要出发去海滩的时候使用能够使你马上展现出粉嫩好气色。</p><p><strong>重量：</strong>3.4克</p>', '<p>滑石，云母，硬脂酸镁，硬脂酸，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，石蜡油，聚丁烯，微晶蜡，蜂蜡，聚二甲基硅氧烷</p><p>可能含有（+/-）：氧化铁红CI77491，二氧化钛CI77891，氧化铁黑CI77499，氧化铁棕CI77491/92/99，红6号巴茨15850</p>'),
(60, 14, 'CHEER DOU HIGHLIGHT CONTOUR', 'KISS BEAUTY', 'CHICCAGP-1461720966-2154.png', '<p>HydraGel is a revolutionary formula with hybrid gel technology. The ease of a powder with the fresh, natural look of a cream -- HydraGel Blush makes you look like you&#39;re blushing, not like you&#39;re wearing blush. Formulated with beneficial ingredients Shea Butter, Avocado Butter and Jojoba Seed Oil to hydrate the skin while Lavender extract provides luminosity for a fresh, natural-looking flush of pure color.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.11 oz</p>\r\n', '3.12g', '<p>ethylhexyl palmitate, cera alba/beeswax, silica, ricinus communis (castor) seed oil, persea gratissima (avocado) butter, simmondsia chinensis (jojoba) seed oil, butyrospermum parkii (shea) butter, lavandula angustifolia (lavender) flower wax, lavandula stoechas extract, sodium hyaluronate, stearyl glycyrrhetinate, tocopherol, tocopheryl acetate, magnesium ascorbyl phosphate, tetrahexyldecyl ascorbate, caprylic/capric triglyceride, phenoxyethanol, tin oxide, micamay contain (+/-): titanium dioxide (ci 77891), iron oxides (ci 77491, 77492, 77499), carmine (ci 75470), red 7 lake (ci 15850).</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:36:06', '03-KISS-DOU-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 71, 1000, '轮廓突显腮红棒', 'KISS BEAUTY', '<p>HydraGel 采用的是混合凝胶技术新型配方，带有奶油的清新，打造自然妆容&mdash;&mdash;让你看起来更像是脸红了，而不是使用了腮红。有益成分乳木果油，牛油果酱和荷荷芭油配方，薰衣草提取物在滋润肌肤的同时还带着一种淡淡的自然清香。</p><p><strong>重量：</strong>3.12克</p>', '<p>棕榈酸乙基己，阿尔巴/蜂蜡，二氧化硅，蓖麻（蓖麻）籽油，鳄梨（牛油果）黄油，西蒙得木（荷荷巴）种子油，乳油木（乳木果）黄油，薰衣草（薰衣草）花蜡，薰衣草头状提取物，透明质酸钠，硬脂甘草，生育酚，醋酸生育酚，抗坏血酸磷酸镁，抗坏血酸盐，辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯，苯氧乙醇，氧化锡，云母，可能含有：二氧化钛（CI77891），铁的氧化物（CI77491，77492，77499），胭脂红（CI75470），红7色淀（CI15850）。</p>'),
(61, 14, 'Fashion Eye Lashes', 'BAISIDAI', 'CHICCAGP-1461721106-60360.png', '<p>Baisidai #1340 Lashes are perfect for enhancing your eyes for an everyday look. They create the look of full, beautiful lashes. Lightweight and reusable, these lashes are permanently curled, waterproof, comfortable to wear and easy to apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Natural looking</li>\r\n	<li>Enhances eyes</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to apply</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.3 oz</p>\r\n', '8.5g', '<p><strong><span style="font-size:13pt">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family:roboto">100% sterilized natural hair</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:38:26', '03-BAISIDAI-1-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 72, 1000, '时尚假睫毛', 'BAISIDAI', '<p>Baisidai 1340 号睫毛自然浓密，拥有它就拥有了你梦寐以求的浓眉大眼，永久卷曲，无重感，可重复使用，防水，操作简单，带上后几乎感受不到它的存在。</p><ul>	<li>简约自然</li>	<li>提亮双眼</li>	<li>使用拿捏方便</li></ul><p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>8.5克</p>', '<p><span style="font-family:roboto; font-size:12pt">100% </span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">无菌自然毛发</span></p>'),
(62, 14, 'DOUBLE TROUBLE EYESHADOW IN NEW DRESS', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', 'CHICCAGP-1461721204-92742.png', '<p>Just in time for the Spring, comes Glamour Dolls Double Trouble Eyeshadow in New Dress! From Christmas parties to the ball drop, complete your look with these festive smoky brown shades.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Two smoky brown shades</li>\r\n	<li>Rich pigmentation</li>\r\n	<li>Long-lasting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.5 oz</p>\r\n', '14.17g', '<p><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:roboto">talc, dimethicone, mica, ethlyhexyl palmitate, magnesium stearate, silica, mineral oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, polybutene, phenoxyethanol, ethlyhexylglycerin [may contain (+/-) titanium dioxide, red iron oxide, yellow iron oxide, black iron oxide]</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:40:05', '03-GLAMDOLL-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 69, 1000, '全新包装双色眼影', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', '<p>矿物质粉，完美贴合，不会在眼部形成褶皱；色泽饱满，附着力强，可长时间维持鲜亮色泽，妆效持久，易上色推开；极易上色，打造晕染立体妆容</p><ul>	<li>细腻烟熏双色眉粉</li>	<li>粉质细腻</li>	<li>持久显色，不晕染</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>14.17克</p>', '<p>&nbsp;滑石，二甲基硅氧烷，云母，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，硬脂酸镁，二氧化硅，矿物油，辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯，聚丁烯，苯氧乙醇，乙基己基甘油[可能含有：二氧化钛，氧化铁红，黄色氧化铁，黑色氧化铁氧化]</p>'),
(63, 14, 'DOUBLE LASTING EYELINER', 'BB COLOR', 'CHICCAGP-1461721263-26085.png', '<p>This twist up mechanical eyeliner comes in the shade Wild Child, which is a super bold black. Easy application and great definition!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Long lasting</li>\r\n	<li>Water-resistant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>TIP:&nbsp;<em>Use like a marker, drawing with the tip closest to your lash line for precise definition.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.07 oz</p>\r\n', '1.98g', '<p><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:roboto">ceresin, microcrystalline wax, isododecane, decamethylcyclopentasiloxane, paraffin, isopropyl myristate, phenoxyethanol, methylparaben, bht</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:41:03', '14-BBCOLOR-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 72, 1000, '双头防水眼线笔 ', 'BB COLOR', '<p>来自美国著名电影《野孩子》的符合人体工程力学的眼线笔，酷黑速干，质地细腻。</p><ul>	<li>不晕染，不脱妆</li>	<li>防水防汗</li></ul><p>小贴士：轻轻提拉眼皮，笔尖从眼头位置沿着睫毛根部细腻轻盈勾勒至眼尾即可。</p><p><strong>重量：</strong>1.98克</p>', '<p><span style="color:black; font-family:宋体">纯地蜡，微晶蜡，异十二烷，十甲基环戊硅氧烷，石蜡，肉豆蔻酸异丙酯，苯氧基乙醇，对羟基苯甲酸甲酯</span></p>'),
(64, 14, 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS Creme gel stick', 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS', 'CHICCAGP-1461721438-87467.png', '<p>A new generation cream-gel stick. Formulated to glide on skin with an elegant silky touch, leaving cheeks with a pop of soft color.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cream-gel formula infused with coconut oil</li>\r\n	<li>Superior silky glide-on application</li>\r\n	<li>Soft pop of buildable color</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.04 oz</p>\r\n', '1.13g', '<p>polymethylsilsesquioxane, isononyl isononanoate, dimethicone, polyethylene, synthetic wax, cetearyl ethylhexanoate, dimethicone/vinyl dimethicone crosspolymer, isostearic acid, polyhydroxystearic acid, hydrogenated coconut oil, lecithin, disteardimonium hectorite, tocopherol, propylene carbonate, ascorbyl palmitate, citric acid, gardenia tahitensis flower, bht.may contain: mica, titanium dioxide, iron oxides, red 6, red 7 lake, red 28 lake, yellow 5 lake, blue 1 lake</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:43:58', 'MAR-GB-5416', 'group1,group2,group3', 71, 1000, 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS 奶油棒腮红    ', 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS', '<p>新一代奶油棒腮红，只要在两颊稍稍地涂抹几下，即可化出优雅的淡淡的腮红。<span style="line-height:1.6">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><ul>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">奶油棒腮红由椰子油配制而成</span></li>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">给肌肤如丝般柔滑的质感</span></li>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">温和的可调和色彩Soft pop of buildable color</span></li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong> 1.13克</p>', '<p>聚甲基，异壬酸异壬酯，二甲基硅氧烷，聚乙烯，合成蜡，鲸蜡硬脂乙基己酸酯，二甲基硅氧烷/乙烯基聚二甲基硅氧烷交联聚合物，异硬脂酸，聚羟基酸，氢化椰子油，卵磷脂，二硬脂二甲铵锂蒙脱石，生育酚，碳酸丙烯酯，抗坏血酸棕榈酸酯，柠檬酸，塔希提岛栀子花，可能包含：云母，二氧化钛，氧化铁, 红6、红7色淀，红28色淀，黄5色淀，蓝1色淀。</p>'),
(65, 14, 'DOUBLE MASCARA 1 WHITE ELONGATE 2 BLACK GRAFTING', 'AMAZING DANCE', 'CHICCAGP-1464659749-53100.png', '<p>Clinically shown to increase lash volume by 430%! Developed with leading plastic surgeons to give you luxuriously plump and healthy lashes, this conditioning 5-in-1 formula is so effective, it can replace your mascara, primer, peptide growth serum, tint and curler. Plus, the innovative brush design features a lash ball detailer that gently lifts and curls even the tiniest of lashes.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contains lash-enhancing Peptides, Collagen, Proteins, Acai, Jojoba, Green Tea and Vitamins A, C, E and B5</li>\r\n	<li>Paraben-free, fragrance-free, phthalate-free and sulfate-free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>TIP:&nbsp;<em>To separate lashes and prevent clumping, wiggle the brush back and forth at the roots, then lightly comb up and through to the tips.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.16 oz</p>\r\n', '4.5g', '<p><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:roboto; font-size:16px">water, beeswax, copernicia cerifera (carnauba) wax, dimethicone, pvp, stearic acid, glyceryl stearate se, sorbitan stearate, polybutene, oleic acid, magnesium aluminum silicate, cellulose gum, chlorphenesin, panthenol, ascorbyl palmitate, disodium edta, euterpe oleracea fruit extract, simmondsia chinensis (jojoba) seed oil, cocoyl hydrolyzed collagen, hydrolyzed wheat protein, lauroyl lysine, biotin, serenoa serrulata fruit extract, urtica dioica (nettle) extract, equisetum arvense extract, camellia sinensis (green tea) leaf extract, glycerin, mysristoyl hexapeptide-16, arginine, malus domestica fruit cell culture extract, lecithin, phenoxyethanol, caprylyl glycol, potassium sorbate, hexylene glycol may contain: iron oxides (ci 77499)</span></p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:45:36', '14-AMAS-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 74, 1000, '双头睫毛膏白色拉长黑色嫁接', 'AMAZING DANCE', '<p>临床证明长期使用这款睫毛膏使得睫毛卷曲程度提高了430%！与权威的整形外科医生共同研发的这款采用五合一调节配方的睫毛膏能够带给你梦寐以求地乌黑浓密以及健康生长的睫毛， 它可以取代你的睫毛膏、眼部打底霜以及睫毛增长液、着色笔、 睫毛夹。此外，睫毛刷融合了创意睫毛球设计，即使是最细小的睫毛也能够毫不费劲地上妆着色。</p><ul>	<li>配方包含睫毛增强肽，胶原蛋白，蛋白，阿萨伊，荷荷巴油，绿茶和维生素A，C，E和B5</li>	<li>不含对羟苯甲酸酯，不含香料，不含邻苯二甲酸盐和硫酸盐</li></ul><p>小贴士：为了防止结块以及分离睫毛，使用时轻轻地在睫毛根部来回扭动，然后轻轻地由根部往睫毛生长的方向梳起来。</p><p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>4.5克</p>', '<p>&nbsp;水，蜂蜡，巴西棕榈蜡，二甲基聚硅氧烷，PVP，硬脂酸，硬脂酸甘油酯SE，脱水山梨醇硬脂酸酯，聚丁烯，油酸，硅酸镁铝，纤维素胶，氯苯甘醚，泛醇，棕榈酸抗坏血酸酯，EDTA二钠，尤特普甘蓝果提取物，霍霍巴（荷荷巴）籽油，椰油水解胶原蛋白，水解小麦蛋白，月桂酰赖氨酸，生物素，锯齿石楠果提取物，大荨麻（荨麻）提取物，问荆提取物，茶树（绿茶）叶提取物，甘油，肉豆蔻六肽-16，精氨酸，海棠家蝇果细胞小路TURE提取物，卵磷脂，苯氧基乙醇，辛乙二醇，山梨酸钾，己二醇可以包含：氧化铁（CI77499）</p>'),
(66, 14, 'PROFESSIONAL EYESHADOW MAKUP', 'ALAOUOOUO', 'CHICCAGP-1461721764-96150.png', '<p>Just in time for the spring comes Alaouoouo Quad Eye shadow in Silver and Purple hues! From night time parties to cool daytime events, complete your look with these festive shimmery shades.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Four shimmery shades</li>\r\n	<li>Rich pigmentation</li>\r\n	<li>Long-lasting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.12 oz</p>\r\n', '3.4g', '<p>talc, dimethicone, mica, ethlyhexyl palmitate, magnesium stearate, silica, mineral oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, polybutene, phenoxyethanol, ethlyhexylglycerin [may contain (+/-) titanium dioxide, red iron oxide, yellow iron oxide, black iron oxide]</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:49:25', '12-ALAOU-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 69, 1000, '???????? ', 'ALAOUOOUO', '<p>Alaouooue Quad 银色和紫色色调眼影套盒帮你塑造最美的春季妆容，从晚妆到日妆，这款眼影能够满足你的所有日常妆容需求。</p><ul>	<li>华丽闪烁的四色色调</li>	<li>丰富的色素沉着</li>	<li>持久力强</li></ul><p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>3.4克</p>', '<p>滑石，二甲基硅氧烷，云母，棕榈酸乙基己酯，硬脂酸镁，二氧化硅，矿物油，辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯，聚丁烯，苯氧基乙醇，乙基己基甘油[可能含有二氧化钛，氧化铁红，黄色氧化铁，黑色氧化铁</p>'),
(67, 14, 'NYX JUMBO Lip stick Pencil', 'NYX', 'CHICCAGP-1461722273-97808.png', '<p>Fall in love with this new matte lip pencil. Buttery soft, rich, yet light as air and comfortable with a futuristic vibrant finish. Infused with Vitamin E, and Shea Butter for moisture and antioxidant properties.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Feels as light as air</li>\r\n	<li>Silky soft and smooth</li>\r\n	<li>Contains vitamin E and Shea Tahiti Butter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Chicters who receive this in their Glam Bag will receive the shade Florence Fig or Chile Red.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TIP:</strong>&nbsp;The Color is super build-able, so add a few more layers for a nighttime look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.02 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56g', '<p>sononyl isononanoate, polymethylsilsesquioxane, squalane, hydrogenated polyisobutene, polyethylene, synthetic wax, caprylic/capric triglyceride, c30-45 alkyl dimethicone, dimethicone/vinyl dimethicone crosspolymer, stearalkonium bentonite, cetyl dimethicone, dimethicone, hydrogenated coconut oil, lecithin, propylene carbonate, tocopherol, ascori3yl palmitate, laureth-4, citric acid, gardenia tahitensis flower, tin oxide. may contain: mica, titanium dioxide, iron oxides, manganese violet, red 6, red 7 lake, red 28 lake, yellow 5 lake, blue 1 lake</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 01:57:53', 'MAR-GB-5413', 'group1,group2,group3', 73, 1000, 'NYX JUMBO 蜡笔唇膏', 'NYX', '<p><strong>即刻</strong>爱上这款新型磨砂唇笔。它犹如奶油般丝滑， 易上色且不轻易掉色，犹如空气般轻薄舒适活力四射极富现代感。富含维生素E及乳木果油，滋润保湿，抗氧化。</p><ul>	<li>犹如空气般轻薄</li>	<li>柔软丝滑</li>	<li>富含维生素E及乳木果油</li></ul><p>格南袋中的该款蜡笔唇膏是佛罗伦萨无花果色或是辣椒红色。</p><p><strong>TIP:</strong> 该唇膏颜色可塑性极强，使用者多次上色即可打造完美晚妆。</p><p><strong>重量： </strong>0.56克</p>', '<p>蚕丝油、聚甲基倍半硅氧烷、角鲨烷、氢化聚异丁烯、聚乙烯、合成蜡、辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯、c30-45烷基硅氧烷，硅氧烷/乙烯基硅氧烷聚合物、司拉氯铵膨润土、鲸蜡硅氧烷，硅氧烷，氢化椰子油、卵磷脂、碳酸丙烯酯、维生素E、维生素C棕榈酸脂、月桂醇聚醚-4，柠檬酸，塔希提栀子花，氧化锡。可能还包含：云母、钛白粉、铁氧化物、锰紫、红6、红7色淀、红28色淀、黄5色淀、蓝1色淀</p>'),
(68, 14, 'CLASSIC 3D BLENDER', 'BLEND CLEANSER', 'CHICCAGP-1461722429-76170.png', '<p>The 3D Blender is designed with a slightly more dense texture than other blenders that not only fits the contours of the face but gives the sponge a lengthier life cycle. Ergonomically shaped, 100% latex-free and easy-to-use, these mini miracles make foundation application, contouring, and highlighting a snap! They can be used wet or dry and are completely reusable! Simply wash with soap and water and let dry.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Re-usable</li>\r\n	<li>Can be used wet or dry</li>\r\n	<li>Great for contouring and highlighting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.1 oz</p>\r\n', '2.83g', '<p>hydrophilic polyurethane foam &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:00:29', '11-BLEND3D-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 94, 1000, '经典3D面皂', 'BLEND CLEANSER', '<p>这款经典3D面皂相对于其他普通面皂质地更为致密，在设计在采用了符合面部线条的流线型设计，符合人体工程力学的设计不但更易于清洁，同时也延长了海绵的使用寿命，100%无乳胶添加，易于使用。这些小小的改进使得脸部清洁更加彻底，轮廓更为突显，肤色更加靓丽。面皂可干湿两用并可重复使用，只需简单直接用皂清洁脸部或加水使用。</p><ul>	<li>可重复使用</li>	<li>干湿两用</li>	<li>重塑线条和提亮肤色效果明显</li></ul><p><strong>重量</strong><strong>：</strong>2.83克</p>', '<p>亲水性聚氨酯泡沫</p>'),
(69, 14, 'BROW BRUSH', 'CROWN BRUSH', 'CHICCAGP-1461722460-92009.png', '<p>This single-sided brush is perfectly designed for all your brow needs. The stiff fiber bristles make brow application easy while the cut angle of the brush makes it fit to your brow bone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.1 oz</p>\r\n', '2.83g', '<p>synthetic fibers, wooden handles</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:01:00', '20-CROWNBRUSH-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 70, 1000, '眉刷', 'CROWN BRUSH', '<p>该单面刷能够满足你化眉妆的所有需求，刚性纤维刷毛使用体验更加舒适而刷子特别的切割角度使得其更切合你的眉骨。</p><p><strong>重量：</strong>2.83克</p>', '<p>合成纤维、木制手柄</p>'),
(70, 14, 'BOMBSHELL COSMETICS Mechanical Eyeliner', 'BOMBSHELL COSMETICS', 'CHICCAGP-1461722712-90176.png', '<p>This twist up mechanical eyeliner comes in the shade Wild Child, which is a super bold black. Easy application and great definition!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Long lasting</li>\r\n	<li>Water-resistant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.007 oz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tip:&nbsp;<em>Use like a marker, drawing with the tip closest to your lash line for precise definition.</em></p>\r\n', '0.19 å…‹', '<p>cerise, microcrystalline wax, isododecane, decamethylcyclopentasiloxane, paraffin, isopropyl myristate, phenoxyethanol, methylparaben, bht</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:05:12', 'MAR-GB-5415', 'group1,group2,group3', 72, 1000, 'BOMBSHELL COSMETICS 机械性眼线笔', 'BOMBSHELL COSMETICS', '<p>美国著名电影《野孩子》主角同款眼线笔，是纯黑色眼线笔。使用便捷妆容精致。</p><ul>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">持久力强</span></li>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">防水</span></li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>0.19克</p><p>小贴士：<em>像使用记号笔一样，用笔尖轻轻划过睫毛即可。</em></p>', '<p>樱桃色，微晶蜡，异十二烷，十甲基环戊硅氧烷，石蜡，肉豆蔻酸异丙酯，苯氧基乙醇，对羟基苯甲酸甲酯</p>'),
(71, 14, 'FANTASTIC FOUR SOAP CLASSIC 3D BLENDER', 'BLEND CLEANSER', 'CHICCAGP-1461723002-10726.png', '<p>The 3D Blenders medium and small size with soap, is designed with a slightly more dense texture than other blenders that not only fits the contours of the face but gives the sponge a lengthier life cycle. Ergonomically shaped, 100% latex-free and easy-to-use, these mini miracles make foundation application, contouring, and highlighting a snap! They can be used wet or dry and are completely reusable! Simply wash with soap and water and let dry.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Re-usable</li>\r\n	<li>Can be used wet or dry</li>\r\n	<li>Great for contouring and highlighting</li>\r\n	<li>Small size 3D blend for tight corner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.10 oz</p>\r\n', '2.83g', '<p>hydrophilic polyurethane foam</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:10:02', '11-BLEND3DSET-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 94, 1000, '神奇的四色皂以及3D混合洗面奶 ', 'BLEND CLEANSER', '<p>这款3D大小混合面皂相对于其他普通面皂质地更为致密，在设计在采用了符合面部线条的流线型设计，符合人体工程力学的设计不但更易于清洁，同时也延长了海绵的使用寿命，100%无乳胶添加，易于使用。这些小小的改进使得脸部清洁更加彻底，轮廓更为突显，肤色更加靓丽。面皂可干湿两用并可重复使用，只需简单直接用皂清洁脸部或加水使用。</p><ul>	<li>可重复使用</li>	<li>干湿两用</li>	<li>重塑线条和提亮肤色效果明显</li>	<li>小尺寸3D面皂用于死区清洁</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>2.83克</p>', '<p>亲水性聚氨酯泡沫</p>'),
(72, 14, 'FACE CREAM Face Moisturizer', 'FACE CREAM', 'CHICCAGP-1461723161-82745.png', '<p>This indulgent body cream contains Vitamin E, shea &amp; cocoa butter and organic English honey to soften, nourish and protect your skin. It rubs in and absorbs easily, without the stickiness. It is delicately scented with the lush, aromatic English Leaf fragrance, it&#39;s a classical &lsquo;green floral&rsquo; with an English twist.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nourishes and protects skin</li>\r\n	<li>Uplifting aromatic fragrance</li>\r\n	<li>Pure essential oils and English honey</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.1 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56 g', '<p>Saqua (water), cetearyl alcohol, prunus dulcis (sweet almond oil), glyceryl stearate, butyrospermum parkii (shea butter), theobroma cacao (cocoa butter), phenoxyethanol, sodium stearoyl glutamate, glycerin, parfum (perfume), xanthan gum, citrus sinensis (sweet orange oil), mel (honey), panthenol, tocopherol (vitamin e), coriandrum sativum (coriander oil), ocimum basilicum (basil oil), mentha piperita (peppermint oil), cedrus virginian (cedarwood oil), lavandula angustifolia (lavender oil), caprylyl glycol, decylene glycol, tocopherol, helianthus annuus seed oil</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:12:41', 'MAR-GB-5414', 'group1,group2,group3', 101, 1000, 'FACE CREAM 滋养面霜 ', 'FACE CREAM', '<p>该款神奇滋养面霜富含维他命E、乳木果油、可可油、有机英式蜂蜜，能够有效地滋养保护肌肤，令你的肌肤时刻保持柔和的状态。它有着很好的舒展性，能够轻易地被皮肤吸收而不会感到油腻。它散发着淡淡的优雅的英式叶子的芳香，英式叶子是一种经典的带着英式螺旋状的&ldquo;绿色花朵&rdquo;。</p><ul>	<li>&nbsp;滋养保护肌肤肤</li>	<li>淡淡的怡和清香</li>	<li>特纯精油及英式蜂蜜</li></ul><p><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>重量：</strong></span>0.56 克</p>', '<p>鲸蜡硬脂醇，梅花椇（甜杏仁油），硬脂酸甘油酯，乳油木（牛油），可可（可可脂），苯氧基乙醇，硬脂酰谷氨酸，甘油，香水（香料），黄原胶，甜橙（甜橙油），蜂蜜（蜜），泛醇，生育酚（维生素E），芫荽（芫荽油），罗勒（罗勒油），椒样薄荷（薄荷油），弗吉尼亚雪松（雪松油），薰衣草（薰衣草油），辛乙二醇，癸二醇，生育酚，向日葵子油</p>'),
(73, 14, 'FLAT DEFINER BRUSH 221', 'LUXIE BEAUTY', 'CHICCAGP-1461723279-76407.png', '<p>Luxie Beauty&rsquo;s small tapered blending brush 221 is held by a luscious pink handle and enticing rose gold ferrule. Handcrafted with synthetic bristles, this vegan makeup brush is both cruelty-free and paraben-free. Coated in a revolutionary antibacterial solution, the brush is fresh and clean on the skin. The tight density of the brush creates a precise makeup application. Extremely soft on the skin, this brush is the answer to extreme definition and control.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cruelty and paraben-free</li>\r\n	<li>Vegan</li>\r\n	<li>Coated with Antibacterial Solution</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.5 oz</p>\r\n', '14.17g', '<p>no ingredients</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:14:39', '18-FLATBRUSH221-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 70, 1000, '扁平刷定义者221', 'LUXIE BEAUTY', '<p>这款来自Luxie Beauty&rsquo;s 的小号锥形混合刷由精致优雅的黑色手柄和低调的银色套圈构成，纯手工制作的合成刷毛，无任何防腐济添加以及伤害动物性行为，创新抗菌溶液涂层，刷毛十分自然柔软亲肤。细密的刷毛能够轻易化出精致无比的妆容， 这款刷子就是对高端控制的最好诠释。</p><ul>	<li>无任何防腐济添加以及伤害动物性行为</li>	<li>纯素主义者（未使用动物皮革）</li>	<li>抗菌溶液涂层</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>14.17克</p>', '<p>无</p>'),
(74, 14, 'PEONY COSMETICS Eye Shadow Quad', 'PEONY COSMETICS', 'CHICCAGP-1461723398-97588.png', '<p>A highly pigmented palette of four rich, after-dark shades in a nourishing, natural base that keeps it blend-able &amp; velvety smooth. These wearable shadows are formulated with silicon-coated micronized pigments &amp; healthy kaolin clay for a seamless, silky texture that lasts up to 8 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pure Kaolin Clay helps absorb excess oil</li>\r\n	<li>Fragrance-Free</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;No Parabens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.1 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56g', '<p>talc**, mica**, ethylhexyl palmitate**, zinc stearate, silica**, kaolin**, phenoxyethanol. [+/- (may contain /peut contenir) mica**, titanium dioxide (ci 77891)**, iron oxides (ci 77491, ci 77492, ci 77499)**, blue 1 lake (ci 42090)] *organic (bio) **natural (d&rsquo;origine naturelle)</p>\r\n', '2016-04-27 02:16:38', 'MAR-GB-5414', 'group1,group2,group3', 69, 1000, 'PEONY COSMETICS 四色眼影', 'PEONY COSMETICS', '<p>高色素四色眼影，后暗色滋养调中，天然的配方能够与柔滑滋养，自然的高度色素调色。这款四色眼影由粉状的聚硅氧烷配制而成，健康高岭给予其柔滑的质感，持续时间可长达8小时。</p><ul>	<li>&nbsp;纯高岭土可帮助吸收多余油脂</li>	<li>无香型</li>	<li>&nbsp;无对羟基苯甲酸酯</li></ul><p><strong>重量：&nbsp;</strong>0.56g</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>滑石，云母，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，硬脂酸锌，二氧化硅，高岭土，苯氧基乙醇。 [+/-（可能包含）云母，二氧化钛（CI77891），氧化铁（CI77491，CI77492，CI77499），蓝1色淀（CI42090）] 天然有机（生物）（d&rsquo;origine naturelle）</p>'),
(75, 15, 'PEONY COSMETICS Eye Shadow Quad', 'PEONY COSMETICS', 'CHICCAGP-1464657916-42913.png', '<p>A highly pigmented palette of four rich, after-dark shades in a nourishing, natural base that keeps it blend-able &amp; velvety smooth. These wearable shadows are formulated with silicon-coated micronized pigments &amp; healthy kaolin clay for a seamless, silky texture that lasts up to 8 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pure Kaolin Clay helps absorb excess oil</li>\r\n	<li>Fragrance-Free</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;No Parabens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.1 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56g', '<p>talc**, mica**, ethylhexyl palmitate**, zinc stearate, silica**, kaolin**, phenoxyethanol. [+/- (may contain /peut contenir) mica**, titanium dioxide (ci 77891)**, iron oxides (ci 77491, ci 77492, ci 77499)**, blue 1 lake (ci 42090)] *organic (bio) **natural (d&rsquo;origine naturelle)</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:25:16', 'MAR-GB-5414', 'group1,group2,group3', 69, 1000, 'PEONY COSMETICS 四色眼影', 'PEONY COSMETICS', '<p>高色素四色眼影，后暗色滋养调中，天然的配方能够与柔滑滋养，自然的高度色素调色。这款四色眼影由粉状的聚硅氧烷配制而成，健康高岭给予其柔滑的质感，持续时间可长达8小时。</p><ul>	<li>&nbsp;纯高岭土可帮助吸收多余油脂</li>	<li>无香型</li>	<li>&nbsp;无对羟基苯甲酸酯</li></ul><p><strong>重量：&nbsp;</strong>0.56g</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>滑石，云母，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，硬脂酸锌，二氧化硅，高岭土，苯氧基乙醇。 [+/-（可能包含）云母，二氧化钛（CI77891），氧化铁（CI77491，CI77492，CI77499），蓝1色淀（CI42090）] 天然有机（生物）（d&rsquo;origine naturelle）</p>'),
(76, 15, 'FLAT DEFINER BRUSH 221', 'LUXIE BEAUTY', 'CHICCAGP-1464658163-64579.png', '<p>Luxie Beauty&rsquo;s small tapered blending brush 221 is held by a luscious pink handle and enticing rose gold ferrule. Handcrafted with synthetic bristles, this vegan makeup brush is both cruelty-free and paraben-free. Coated in a revolutionary antibacterial solution, the brush is fresh and clean on the skin. The tight density of the brush creates a precise makeup application. Extremely soft on the skin, this brush is the answer to extreme definition and control.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cruelty and paraben-free</li>\r\n	<li>Vegan</li>\r\n	<li>Coated with Antibacterial Solution</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.5 oz</p>\r\n', '14.17g', '<p>no ingredients</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:29:23', '18-FLATBRUSH221-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 70, 1000, '扁平刷定义者221', 'LUXIE BEAUTY', '<p>这款来自Luxie Beauty&rsquo;s 的小号锥形混合刷由精致优雅的黑色手柄和低调的银色套圈构成，纯手工制作的合成刷毛，无任何防腐济添加以及伤害动物性行为，创新抗菌溶液涂层，刷毛十分自然柔软亲肤。细密的刷毛能够轻易化出精致无比的妆容， 这款刷子就是对高端控制的最好诠释。</p><ul>	<li>无任何防腐济添加以及伤害动物性行为</li>	<li>纯素主义者（未使用动物皮革）</li>	<li>抗菌溶液涂层</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>14.17克</p>', '<p>无</p>'),
(77, 15, 'FACE CREAM Face Moisturizer', 'FACE CREAM', 'CHICCAGP-1464658453-53492.png', '<p>This indulgent body cream contains Vitamin E, shea &amp; cocoa butter and organic English honey to soften, nourish and protect your skin. It rubs in and absorbs easily, without the stickiness. It is delicately scented with the lush, aromatic English Leaf fragrance, it&#39;s a classical &lsquo;green floral&rsquo; with an English twist.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nourishes and protects skin</li>\r\n	<li>Uplifting aromatic fragrance</li>\r\n	<li>Pure essential oils and English honey</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.1 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56 g', '<p>Saqua (water), cetearyl alcohol, prunus dulcis (sweet almond oil), glyceryl stearate, butyrospermum parkii (shea butter), theobroma cacao (cocoa butter), phenoxyethanol, sodium stearoyl glutamate, glycerin, parfum (perfume), xanthan gum, citrus sinensis (sweet orange oil), mel (honey), panthenol, tocopherol (vitamin e), coriandrum sativum (coriander oil), ocimum basilicum (basil oil), mentha piperita (peppermint oil), cedrus virginian (cedarwood oil), lavandula angustifolia (lavender oil), caprylyl glycol, decylene glycol, tocopherol, helianthus annuus seed oil</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:34:13', 'MAR-GB-5414', 'group1,group2,group3', 101, 1000, 'FACE CREAM 滋养面霜 ', 'FACE CREAM', '<p>该款神奇滋养面霜富含维他命E、乳木果油、可可油、有机英式蜂蜜，能够有效地滋养保护肌肤，令你的肌肤时刻保持柔和的状态。它有着很好的舒展性，能够轻易地被皮肤吸收而不会感到油腻。它散发着淡淡的优雅的英式叶子的芳香，英式叶子是一种经典的带着英式螺旋状的&ldquo;绿色花朵&rdquo;。</p><ul>	<li>&nbsp;滋养保护肌肤肤</li>	<li>淡淡的怡和清香</li>	<li>特纯精油及英式蜂蜜</li></ul><p><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>重量：</strong></span>0.56 克</p>', '<p>鲸蜡硬脂醇，梅花椇（甜杏仁油），硬脂酸甘油酯，乳油木（牛油），可可（可可脂），苯氧基乙醇，硬脂酰谷氨酸，甘油，香水（香料），黄原胶，甜橙（甜橙油），蜂蜜（蜜），泛醇，生育酚（维生素E），芫荽（芫荽油），罗勒（罗勒油），椒样薄荷（薄荷油），弗吉尼亚雪松（雪松油），薰衣草（薰衣草油），辛乙二醇，癸二醇，生育酚，向日葵子油</p>'),
(78, 15, 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS Creme gel stick', 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS', 'CHICCAGP-1464658595-94304.png', '<p>A new generation cream-gel stick. Formulated to glide on skin with an elegant silky touch, leaving cheeks with a pop of soft color.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cream-gel formula infused with coconut oil</li>\r\n	<li>Superior silky glide-on application</li>\r\n	<li>Soft pop of buildable color</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.04 oz</p>\r\n', '1.13g', '<p>polymethylsilsesquioxane, isononyl isononanoate, dimethicone, polyethylene, synthetic wax, cetearyl ethylhexanoate, dimethicone/vinyl dimethicone crosspolymer, isostearic acid, polyhydroxystearic acid, hydrogenated coconut oil, lecithin, disteardimonium hectorite, tocopherol, propylene carbonate, ascorbyl palmitate, citric acid, gardenia tahitensis flower, bht.may contain: mica, titanium dioxide, iron oxides, red 6, red 7 lake, red 28 lake, yellow 5 lake, blue 1 lake</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:36:35', 'MAR-GB-5416', 'group1,group2,group3', 71, 1000, 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS 奶油棒腮红    ', 'SESE FACE STUDIO COSMETICS', '<p>新一代奶油棒腮红，只要在两颊稍稍地涂抹几下，即可化出优雅的淡淡的腮红。<span style="line-height:1.6">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><ul>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">奶油棒腮红由椰子油配制而成</span></li>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">给肌肤如丝般柔滑的质感</span></li>	<li><span style="line-height:1.6">温和的可调和色彩Soft pop of buildable color</span></li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong> 1.13克</p>', '<p>聚甲基，异壬酸异壬酯，二甲基硅氧烷，聚乙烯，合成蜡，鲸蜡硬脂乙基己酸酯，二甲基硅氧烷/乙烯基聚二甲基硅氧烷交联聚合物，异硬脂酸，聚羟基酸，氢化椰子油，卵磷脂，二硬脂二甲铵锂蒙脱石，生育酚，碳酸丙烯酯，抗坏血酸棕榈酸酯，柠檬酸，塔希提岛栀子花，可能包含：云母，二氧化钛，氧化铁, 红6、红7色淀，红28色淀，黄5色淀，蓝1色淀。</p>'),
(79, 15, 'Fashion Eye Lashes', 'BAISIDAI', 'CHICCAGP-1464658708-54815.png', '<p>Baisidai #1340 Lashes are perfect for enhancing your eyes for an everyday look. They create the look of full, beautiful lashes. Lightweight and reusable, these lashes are permanently curled, waterproof, comfortable to wear and easy to apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Natural looking</li>\r\n	<li>Enhances eyes</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to apply</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.3 oz</p>\r\n', '8.5g', '<p><strong><span style="font-size:13pt">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family:roboto">100% sterilized natural hair</span></p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:38:28', '03-BAISIDAI-1-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 72, 1000, '时尚假睫毛', 'BAISIDAI', '<p>Baisidai 1340 号睫毛自然浓密，拥有它就拥有了你梦寐以求的浓眉大眼，永久卷曲，无重感，可重复使用，防水，操作简单，带上后几乎感受不到它的存在。</p><ul>	<li>简约自然</li>	<li>提亮双眼</li>	<li>使用拿捏方便</li></ul><p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>8.5克</p>', '<p><span style="font-family:roboto; font-size:12pt">100% </span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">无菌自然毛发</span></p>'),
(80, 15, 'CONCEALER BRUSH', 'BEAUTIFUL PARIS', 'CHICCAGP-1464658868-12802.png', '<p><strong>DESCRIPTION</strong>&nbsp;This concealer brush is perfect for applying liquids and creams for a smoother, more flawless concealer application. It&rsquo;s also ideal for covering scars and imperfections as well as meticulously camouflaging dark circles. It comes with a handcrafted brush that enables beautiful and easy makeup applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Very thin tapered tip ensures accurate application and seamless results</li>\r\n	<li>Firm yet soft synthetic fibers bundled closely together</li>\r\n	<li>Eco friendly matt black wooden handles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.3 oz</p>\r\n', '8.5g', '<p>synthetic fibers, wooden handles</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:41:08', '19-BEAUCONC-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 70, 1000, '抗菌遮瑕刷', 'BEAUTIFUL PARIS', '<p>这款遮瑕刷可用于液体性化妆品和面霜，有助于帮你化出精致无瑕的妆容。它不仅能够用于遮盖脸部斑点瑕疵，还可用于打造精致迷彩妆。一支简单的遮瑕刷能够带给你更加完美的妆容体验。</p><ul>	<li>尖细的锥形刷头使用起来更加便捷使得妆容也更为精致。</li>	<li>合成纤维刷毛柔软且牢固不掉毛</li>	<li>生态环保亚光木柄</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>8.5克</p>', '<p>合成纤维、木制手柄</p>'),
(81, 15, 'DOUBLE TROUBLE EYESHADOW IN NEW DRESS', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', 'CHICCAGP-1464659176-34549.png', '<p>Just in time for the Spring, comes Glamour Dolls Double Trouble Eyeshadow in New Dress! From Christmas parties to the ball drop, complete your look with these festive smoky brown shades.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Two smoky brown shades</li>\r\n	<li>Rich pigmentation</li>\r\n	<li>Long-lasting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>0.5 oz</p>\r\n', '14.17g', '<p><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:roboto">talc, dimethicone, mica, ethlyhexyl palmitate, magnesium stearate, silica, mineral oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, polybutene, phenoxyethanol, ethlyhexylglycerin [may contain (+/-) titanium dioxide, red iron oxide, yellow iron oxide, black iron oxide]</span></p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:46:16', '03-GLAMDOLL-2016GB', 'group1,group2,group3', 69, 1000, '全新包装双色眼影', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', '<p>矿物质粉，完美贴合，不会在眼部形成褶皱；色泽饱满，附着力强，可长时间维持鲜亮色泽，妆效持久，易上色推开；极易上色，打造晕染立体妆容</p><ul>	<li>细腻烟熏双色眉粉</li>	<li>粉质细腻</li>	<li>持久显色，不晕染</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>14.17克</p>', '<p>&nbsp;滑石，二甲基硅氧烷，云母，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，硬脂酸镁，二氧化硅，矿物油，辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯，聚丁烯，苯氧乙醇，乙基己基甘油[可能含有：二氧化钛，氧化铁红，黄色氧化铁，黑色氧化铁氧化]</p>'),
(82, 15, 'NYX JUMBO Lip stick Pencil', 'NYX', 'CHICCAGP-1464659245-11116.png', '<p>Fall in love with this new matte lip pencil. Buttery soft, rich, yet light as air and comfortable with a futuristic vibrant finish. Infused with Vitamin E, and Shea Butter for moisture and antioxidant properties.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Feels as light as air</li>\r\n	<li>Silky soft and smooth</li>\r\n	<li>Contains vitamin E and Shea Tahiti Butter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Chicters who receive this in their Glam Bag will receive the shade Florence Fig or Chile Red.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TIP:</strong>&nbsp;The Color is super build-able, so add a few more layers for a nighttime look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT:&nbsp;</strong>.02 oz</p>\r\n', '0.56g', '<p>sononyl isononanoate, polymethylsilsesquioxane, squalane, hydrogenated polyisobutene, polyethylene, synthetic wax, caprylic/capric triglyceride, c30-45 alkyl dimethicone, dimethicone/vinyl dimethicone crosspolymer, stearalkonium bentonite, cetyl dimethicone, dimethicone, hydrogenated coconut oil, lecithin, propylene carbonate, tocopherol, ascori3yl palmitate, laureth-4, citric acid, gardenia tahitensis flower, tin oxide. may contain: mica, titanium dioxide, iron oxides, manganese violet, red 6, red 7 lake, red 28 lake, yellow 5 lake, blue 1 lake</p>\r\n', '2016-05-31 01:47:26', 'MAR-GB-5413', 'group1,group2,group3', 73, 1000, 'NYX JUMBO 蜡笔唇膏', 'NYX', '<p><strong>即刻</strong>爱上这款新型磨砂唇笔。它犹如奶油般丝滑， 易上色且不轻易掉色，犹如空气般轻薄舒适活力四射极富现代感。富含维生素E及乳木果油，滋润保湿，抗氧化。</p><ul>	<li>犹如空气般轻薄</li>	<li>柔软丝滑</li>	<li>富含维生素E及乳木果油</li></ul><p>格南袋中的该款蜡笔唇膏是佛罗伦萨无花果色或是辣椒红色。</p><p><strong>TIP:</strong> 该唇膏颜色可塑性极强，使用者多次上色即可打造完美晚妆。</p><p><strong>重量： </strong>0.56克</p>', '<p>蚕丝油、聚甲基倍半硅氧烷、角鲨烷、氢化聚异丁烯、聚乙烯、合成蜡、辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯、c30-45烷基硅氧烷，硅氧烷/乙烯基硅氧烷聚合物、司拉氯铵膨润土、鲸蜡硅氧烷，硅氧烷，氢化椰子油、卵磷脂、碳酸丙烯酯、维生素E、维生素C棕榈酸脂、月桂醇聚醚-4，柠檬酸，塔希提栀子花，氧化锡。可能还包含：云母、钛白粉、铁氧化物、锰紫、红6、红7色淀、红28色淀、黄5色淀、蓝1色淀</p>');
