(3, 'First Offer Product', 'Reparing Macadamia Oil Trio', '1-1457596714-19363.jpg', 24.00, 33.00, '2016-03-31', '<h2><strong>Repairing Macadamia Oil Trio</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\nLet your hair reap the benefits of the other nut: macadamia!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why we&rsquo;re obsessed:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The macadamia oil in these products works to hydrate and promote shine, while bamboo extract strengths and smooths, making it the perfect combo for healthy, silky hair!</li>\r\n	<li>The shampoo removes dead cells, build-up and pollutants to reveal a natural luster. Plus, it is safe on color treated hair.</li>\r\n	<li>This light-weight conditioner nourishes dry, overworked hair while reducing frizz and softening your strands.</li>\r\n	<li>The oil treatment quickly penetrates hair to combat damage and dryness for stronger, healthier looking hair.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full-size trio includes:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Repairing Macadamia Oil Sulfate Free Shampoo</li>\r\n	<li>Repairing Macadamia Oil Sulfate Free Conditioner</li>\r\n	<li>Repairing Macadamia Oil Treatment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong><span style="color:black; font-family:roboto">Repairing Macadamia Oil Sulfate Free Shampoo:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="color:black; font-family:roboto">water, sodium c14 16 olefin sulfonate, cocamidopropyl betaine, cocamide mea, glycerin, divinyldimethicone/dimethicone copolymer, c12 13 pareth 3, c12 13 pareth 23, amodimethicone, cetrimonium chloride, trideceth 12, macadamia ternifolia seed oil, bambusa vulgaris leaf/stem extract, glycol stearate, polyquaternium 55, sodium chloride, hydrolyzed keratin, polyquaternium 10, guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, parfum (fragrance), butyrospermum parkii (shea butter), hydrolyzed wheat protein, keratin, punica granatum (pomegranate) extract, soja (soybean) oil, vitis vinifera (grape) seed oil, sodium pca, sodium lactate, arginine, aspartic acid, pca, glycine, alanine, 