(12, 'BlendCleanser', 'FANTASTIC FOUR SOAP AND 3D BLEND CLEANSER', 'QQ20160302-1-1456912617-81354.png', 0.01, 10.00, '2016-09-30', '<p>The 3D Blenders medium and small size with soap, is designed with a slightly more dense texture than other blenders that not only fits the contours of the face but gives the sponge a lengthier life cycle. Ergonomically shaped, 100% latex-free and easy-to-use, these mini miracles make foundation application, contouring, and highlighting a snap! They can be used wet or dry and are completely reusable! Simply wash with soap and water and let dry.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Re-usable</li>\r\n	<li>Can be used wet or dry</li>\r\n	<li>Great for contouring and highlighting</li>\r\n	<li>Small size 3D blend for tight corner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>0.10 oz</p>\r\n', '<p><span style="font-family:roboto">hydrophilic polyurethane foam</span></p>\r\n', '2016-07-27 02:01:59', 'BlendCleanser', '神奇的四色皂以及3D混合洗面奶', '<p>这款3D大小混合面皂相对于其他普通面皂质地更为致密，在设计在采用了符合面部线条的流线型设计，符合人体工程力学的设计不但更易于清洁，同时也延长了海绵的使用寿命，100%无乳胶添加，易于使用。这些小小的改进使得脸部清洁更加彻底，轮廓更为突显，肤色更加靓丽。面皂可干湿两用并可重复使用，只需简单直接用皂清洁脸部或加水使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>可重复使用</li>\r\n	<li>干湿两用</li>\r\n	<li>重塑线条和提亮肤色效果明显</li>\r\n	<li>小尺寸3D面皂用于死区清洁</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>重量：</strong>2.83克</p>\r\n', '<p><span style="color:black; font-family:simsun">亲水性聚氨酯泡沫</span></p>\r\n', 0.10, '0', ''),
