(14, 'the Balm Cosmetics', 'NUDE-dude', '2-1457593943-52923.png', 38.00, 33.00, '2016-03-31', '<h2><strong>Introducing the Balm&#39;s latest addition to the Nude series...</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Nude Dude!</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Why we&rsquo;re obsessed:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can Get a quick look using any combination of these triple-milled shadows or dress up your look by adding water to transform your favorite shades into loyal liners. This total package includes 12 full-bodied shadows that can be worn alone or layered for added intensity, so go ahead and cover (or uncover) your eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gorgeous highlighter, shadow and shimmer</li>\r\n	<li>Universally flattering shade</li>\r\n	<li>Cruelty-free and contains no parabens or talc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>SHIMMER SHADOWS INGREDIENTS: MICA, DIMETHICONE, SYNTHETIC WAX, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, BORON NITRATE, PTFE, POLYETHYLENE, KAOLIN, ISOEICOSANE, SILICA, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, SODIUM DEHYDROACETATE, CALCIUM ALUMINUM BOROSILICATE. MAY CONTAIN / PEUT CONTENIR [+/- TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891). BISMUTH OXYCHLORIDE (CI 77163), IRON OXIDES (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), CARMINE (CI 75470), MANGANESE VIOLET (CI 77742), ULTRAMARINES (CI 77007), YELLOW 5 LAKE (CI 19140)]&nbsp;<br />\r\nMATTE SHADOWS INGREDIENTS: MICA, DIMETHICONE, SYNTHETIC WAX, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, BORON NITRATE, PTFE, POLYETHYLENE, KAOLIN, ISOEICOSANE, SILICA, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, SODIUM DEHYDROACETATE. MAY CONTAIN / PEUT CONTENIR [+/- TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891). BISMUTH OXYCHLORIDE (CI 77163), IRON OXIDES (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), CARMINE (CI 75470), MANGANESE VIOLET (CI 77742), ULTRAMARINES (CI 77007)]</p>\r\n', '2016-03-10 01:39:43', ' the Balm Cosmetics', '裸妆风暴眼影盒', '<h3><strong>The Blam 最新百搭万能裸妆眼影盒：</strong></h3><h3>裸妆风暴眼影盒！</h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>为什么它会令你着迷：</strong></p><p>12种百搭大地色，是眼影，也是眼线。随意搭配使用打造立体、轮廓、深邃的眼部效果。加水使用即可用你喜爱的眼影画出精致的眼线。</p><ul>	<li>集萃三种质地眼影，高光色、亚光色、微闪色</li>	<li>通用裸妆色系、粉质细腻</li>	<li>不含苯甲酸酯类或滑石粉及动物成分</li></ul>', '<p>SHIMMER SHADOWS INGREDIENTS: MICA, DIMETHICONE, SYNTHETIC WAX, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, BORON NITRATE, PTFE, POLYETHYLENE, KAOLIN, ISOEICOSANE, SILICA, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, SODIUM DEHYDROACETATE, CALCIUM ALUMINUM BOROSILICATE. MAY CONTAIN / PEUT CONTENIR [+/- TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891). BISMUTH OXYCHLORIDE (CI 77163), IRON OXIDES (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), CARMINE (CI 75470), MANGANESE VIOLET (CI 77742), ULTRAMARINES (CI 77007), YELLOW 5 LAKE (CI 19140)]&nbsp;<br />\r\nMATTE SHADOWS INGREDIENTS: MICA, DIMETHICONE, SYNTHETIC WAX, CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, BORON NITRATE, PTFE, POLYETHYLENE, KAOLIN, ISOEICOSANE, SILICA, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, SODIUM DEHYDROACETATE. MAY CONTAIN / PEUT CONTENIR [+/- TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891). BISMUTH OXYCHLORIDE (CI 77163), IRON OXIDES (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), CARMINE (CI 75470), MANGANESE VIOLET (CI 77742), ULTRAMARINES (CI 77007)]</p>\r\n', 249.00, '0', ''),
