(18, 'Skinn Cosmetics', 'Skinn Cleansing System', '6-1457581151-79141.jpg', 42.00, 71.00, '2016-03-01', '<h2><strong>Skinn Cleansing System</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\n2 Full-size skincare products that make the perfect morning + night combo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why you&rsquo;ll love it:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Balm Cleanser uses water-free formula to dissolve dirt, makeup, daily grime, pollution and dead skin cells and is perfect for night use.</li>\r\n	<li>The exfoliating cleanser deeply exfoliates and rinses away impurities with a lightweight, yet lavish formula.</li>\r\n	<li>Both cleansers are extra gentle on your skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set includes:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Olive &amp; Enzyme Rich Balm Cleanser</li>\r\n	<li>Sulfate Free Gentle Exfoliating Cleanser</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Olive &amp; Enzyme Rich Balm Cleanser:&nbsp;</strong>citrus aurantium dulcis (orange) fruit extract, carthamus tinctorius (safflower) oleosomes, helianthus annuus (sunflower) seed oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, isopentyldiol, glycerin (vegetable), sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, squalane, papain (papaya enzymes), citrus aurantium amara (bitter orange) flower wax, olea europaea (olive oil), persea gratissima (avocado) oil, calendula officinalis flower extract, manganese gluconate, phenoxyethanol, capryl glycol, ethylhexylglycerin, hexylene glycol, beta carotene</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sulfate Free Gentle Exfoliating Cleanser:&nbsp;</strong>vitis vinifera (grape) fruit extract, sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, cocamidopropyl betaine, coco-glucoside, glyceryl oleate, lavandula hybrida (lavender) oil, melaleuca alternifolia (tea tree) leaf oil, mentha piperita (peppermint) oil, salicylic acid, glycolic acid, malic acid, lactic acid, camellia sinensis (green tea) leaf extract, glycosaminoglycans, magnesium ascorbyl phosphate, ascorbyl palmitate, acrylates copolymer, disodium edta, phenoxyethanol, ethylhexylglycerin</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 oz Balm Cleanser | 4 oz Exfoliating Cleanser</p>\r\n', '2016-03-10 03:39:11', 'Skinn Cosmetics', 'Skinn 清洁套装', '<h2><strong>Skinn </strong><strong>清洁套装</strong>&nbsp;<br />2款原装早晚二合一护肤品</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>为什么如此受到新老顾客追捧：</strong></p><ul>	<li style="margin-left: 35.7pt;">该洁面乳膏采用的是不含水配方，它可以有效溶解脸上的污垢、化妆品、灰尘、污染物和死皮细胞从而达到充分清洁的目的，适合夜间使用</li>	<li style="margin-left: 35.7pt;">轻便型去角质洗面奶采用的是独家奢华配方，它能够深层次有效地袪除角质和污垢。</li>	<li style="margin-left: 35.7pt;">两款洗面奶都属于温和型，使用后不会有紧绷感。</li></ul><p><strong>该系列产品包括：</strong></p><ul>	<li style="margin-left: 35.7pt;">丰富型橄榄和酶洁面乳膏</li>	<li style="margin-left: 35.7pt;">无硫酸盐温和去角质洁面乳</li></ul>', '<p><strong>丰富型橄榄和酶洁面乳膏：</strong>&nbsp;citrus aurantium dulcis (orange) fruit extract, carthamus tinctorius (safflower) oleosomes, helianthus annuus (sunflower) seed oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, isopentyldiol, glycerin (vegetable), sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, squalane, papain (papaya enzymes), citrus aurantium amara (bitter orange) flower wax, olea europaea (olive oil), persea gratissima (avocado) oil, calendula officinalis flower extract, manganese gluconate, phenoxyethanol, capryl glycol, ethylhexylglycerin, hexylene glycol, beta carotene</p><p><strong>无硫酸盐温和去角质洁面乳：</strong>&nbsp;vitis vinifera (grape) fruit extract, sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, cocamidopropyl betaine, coco-glucoside, glyceryl oleate, lavandula hybrida (lavender) oil, melaleuca alternifolia (tea tree) leaf oil, mentha piperita (peppermint) oil, salicylic acid, glycolic acid, malic acid, lactic acid, camellia sinensis (green tea) leaf extract, glycosaminoglycans, magnesium ascorbyl phosphate, ascorbyl palmitate, acrylates copolymer, disodium edta, phenoxyethanol, ethylhexylglycerin</p><p>洁面乳膏113g | 去角质洁面乳113g</p>', 249.00, '0', ''),
(19, 'Trust fund Beauty', 'Money is No object Trio', '7-1457581862-2656.jpg', 45.00, 60.00, '2016-03-01', '<h2><strong>Money Is No Object Trio&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nGrab this Pantone-inspired trio to keep your nails on trend all year long</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why you&rsquo;ll love this brand:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All of their nail polishes are super long-lasting and chip-resistant.</li>\r\n	<li>These beautiful colors are deeply saturated!</li>\r\n	<li>Their formula is 7-free and vegan - double score!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shades includes:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Money Buys Happiness (baby pink)</li>\r\n	<li>Money Shot (gold glitter)</li>\r\n	<li>What&rsquo;s a Budget? (sea foam blue)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><span style="color:black; font-family:roboto">Butyl Acetate, Ethyl Acetate, Nitrocellulose, Acetyl Tributyl Citrate, Adipic Acid/ Neopentyl Glycol/ Trimellitic Anhydride Copolymer, Isopropyl Alcohol, Stearalkonium Bentonite, Acrylates Copolymer, Styrene/ Acrylates, Copolymer, May Contain: CI 77891, CI 19140, CI 15850, CI 15850, CI 15880, CI 77491,_CI 77499, CI 77510, CI 77163 Polyethylene Terephthalate, Aluminium Powder, Mica, Dibenzoate</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#AAAAAA; font-family:roboto">Nail Polish 3 x .57 oz</span></p>\r\n', '2016-03-10 03:51:02', 'Trust fund Beauty', '钱不是问题三重奏', '<h2><strong>钱不是问题三重奏</strong>&nbsp;<br />抓住这一潘通灵感三重奏你就抓住了整年的指甲流行趋势</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>为什么如此受到新老顾客追捧：</strong></p><ul>	<li>所有的指甲油都具有抗脱落性及超持久性</li>	<li>所有的指甲油颜色都是深度饱和型的，色泽十分丰富耐看</li>	<li>所有指甲油均采用纯植物配方且均属于7无（无羟基苯甲酸酯，邻苯二甲酸酯（邻苯二甲酸二丁酯），甲苯，二甲苯，樟脑，甲醛，树脂，）的无毒指甲油</li></ul><p><strong>产品系列包括</strong></p><ul>	<li>钱真的可以买到幸福 （淡粉色）</li>	<li>资拍摄（闪光金色）</li>	<li>何为预算？（海洋泡沫蓝色）</li></ul>', '<p>Butyl Acetate, Ethyl Acetate, Nitrocellulose, Acetyl Tributyl Citrate, Adipic Acid/ Neopentyl Glycol/ Trimellitic Anhydride Copolymer, Isopropyl Alcohol, Stearalkonium Bentonite, Acrylates Copolymer, Styrene/ Acrylates, Copolymer, May