(1, 'About Us', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-8 text-left">\r\n<p>One of the most asked beauty question many women in China and around the world&nbsp;ask is: &quot;What are the right beauty products for me? &ldquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With infinite beauty product combinations in the marketplace, choosing the best items for your needs can be a challenge! That was why <strong>James</strong> created&nbsp;<strong>Chicca Blu.</strong> James and his team of stylists have selected products they love, for you to try.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each month, subscribers will receive a beautiful Glam Bag with&nbsp;<strong>deluxe samples</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>full-sized beauty products.</strong> Members can watch and play along with the stylists with the same products that they are using.&nbsp;<strong>All for only $15 a month</strong>!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So go ahead, take the beauty quiz, and get your first Glam Bag!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a class="btn btn-pink btn-block btnMd" href="http://chicca-blu.com/register" style="max-width:220px;color:#fff; background:#e72d9e;">Become a Member</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-4">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12 text-left">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="font-bold">Chiccablu Mailing Address:</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Pegasus Technology Information LTD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Room 701, Unit 1, Building B,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kexing Science Park, Keyuan Road, Science Park,</p>\r\nNanshan District, Shenzhen City. PRC.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2016-07-19 09:04:26', '关于我们', '<div class="row"><div class="col-sm-8 text-left"><p>许多中国和世界其他国家的女人最常问的一个美容问题就是：什么样的美容产品适合我？</p><p>伴随市场出现的无限量的美容产品组合，需要根据您的需求选择最适合您的产品确实是一种挑战！这就是为什么<strong>James</strong> 创造了<strong>Chicca Blu</strong>, <strong>James </strong>和他的设计师们选择了他们钟爱的产品供您尝试使用。</p><p>每个月，订阅者将会收到一个装有高级样品的<strong>精美产品套餐袋</strong>及<strong>完整的美容产品</strong>。会员们可以看到设计师们如何使用跟您一样的产品的相关视频。<strong>每个月推出的所有产品套餐只需要</strong><strong>88</strong><strong>元</strong>。</p><p>所以快来参与吧！做个简短的美容问卷调查，开启您的第一个精美美容套餐之旅。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><a class="btn btn-pink btn-block btnMd" href="http://chicca-blu.com/register" style="max-width:220px;color:#fff;background:#e72d9e;">关于我们</a></div><div class="col-sm-4">&nbsp;</div></div><hr /><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12 text-left"><p>&nbsp;</p><div class="font-bold">Chiccablu邮寄地址：</div><div><p>深圳市佩格索斯科技信息有限公司</p><p>深圳市南山区科技园区科苑路科兴科学</p><p>园B栋1单元701.</p><p>客服热线： 0755－23180308</p><p>传真号码：0755 - 23180302</p><p>邮箱地址：chiccablu@gmail.com</p></div>&nbsp;<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div>'),
(2, 'COMMUNITY GUIDELINES', '<div class="row text-left margin-bot">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="padding">\r\n<p>Welcome to&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu&#39;s</strong>&nbsp;guidelines for our online community, which includes all the places where&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu</strong>&nbsp;lives on the web, such as chiccablu.com, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, and Pinterest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>chiccablu</strong>&nbsp;is about much more than just beauty products. We&#39;re about celebrating beauty of all forms in the world. We&#39;re about motivation, inspiration, and fostering a community that expresses both inner and outer radiance. We want to create a fun and safe place (on our website, on&nbsp;<a href="http://www.facebook.com/chiccablu" target="_blank">Facebook</a>, and elsewhere) for&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>&nbsp;to share their passions, ideas, experiences, and more. We&#39;re all here to support one another and learn new things, so please be on your best behavior! Remember:&nbsp;<strong><em>beauty is as beauty does</em></strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WHAT TO DO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be positive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in supporting one another in the most positive way possible. Treat others as you would like to be treated. Non-constructive negativity (ranting, excessive venting, snide commentary) doesn&#39;t add value to the &nbsp;community experience, so please do not disparage other&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu Stylists</strong>, products, brands, or&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu</strong>&nbsp;in general. We always welcome your feedback, and there&#39;s nothing wrong with a healthy debate or discussion, but please keep it constructive and polite! Your words will come across much more effectively if you voice them in a positive way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Help your fellow chicsters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We love seeing&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>&nbsp;help one another. Advice, tips, and tricks are always appreciated from one&nbsp;<strong>chicster</strong>&nbsp;to another. This is your community, so we need your partnership to keep the conversation fun, intelligent, and drama-free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Show us what you got!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We want to see your videos, photos, and looks, and we love hearing your voice. Define yourself and be an original!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Share with us what&#39;s inspiring you across the world wide web, but remember, if it&#39;s not something you&#39;ve created, get permission to share and give credit where credit&#39;s due!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us directly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you ever have an issue, question, or suggestion, the best and fastest way to get a response is to email&nbsp;<strong>chiccabluCare</strong>. In fact, due to privacy reasons, we cannot use public forums to resolve many individual issues. We&#39;ll do our best to support you and answer general questions wherever we can, but it is always best to&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/community-guidelines" target="_blank">e-mail chiccabluCare</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/community-guidelines">tweet @chiccabluCare</a><a name="OLE_LINK2"></a>&nbsp;so they can investigate and help you out!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be respectful.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&#39;re here to make discoveries, share knowledge, and celebrate our love for all things beauty. It&#39;s important we communicate to each other with grace and suavity (yes, that&#39;s a word!). If you want respect, give it first. Every&nbsp;<strong>chicster</strong>&nbsp;has a right to participate on our website and social media channels without being ridiculed or belittled (for example, complaining about other people&#39;s complaints just creates more complaining!).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have&nbsp;<strong>ipsters</strong>&nbsp;from all walks of life, so be sensitive by avoiding profanity (the 7 dirty words are not allowed), sexually explicit content, and anything that could potentially offend your fellow&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu Stylists</strong>&nbsp;are a crucial part of our community, and always work hard to inspire you with amazing content. Please remember they are human beings -- just like you -- who deserve to be treated with kindness and respect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a no-tolerance policy for abuse toward community members. Any comment that is negative, critical, judgmental, or disparaging in any sense toward an individual stylist, our stylists as a group, or a fellow&nbsp;<strong>chicster</strong>&nbsp;will be deleted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please extend respect not only to your fellow&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu Stylists</strong>, but also to the&nbsp;<strong>chiccabluCare</strong>&nbsp;team! They&#39;re real people, here to provide you with stellar service and support, so be nice. They&#39;ll always treat you with dignity and kindness, so we expect you to do the same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WHAT NOT TO DO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t be rude, cruel, or intolerant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Harassing, bullying, or intimidating other&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>, or defaming the community,<strong>chiccablu Stylists</strong>, and company as a whole, is a major no-no. There&#39;s nothing worse than someone who ruins a good party by being spiteful and mean-spirited. Don&#39;t be that person!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We do not tolerate name-calling; personal, professional, or religious attacks or threats; racist or sexist comments; hate speech (or any comments that could be interpreted as such); demeaning remarks based on personal appearance, race, ethnicity, religion, gender, gender identity, disability, or sexual orientation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t spam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you share content with fellow&nbsp;<strong>chicsters</strong>, please provide context, don&#39;t post the same thing more than once, and don&#39;t share purely commercial links (like affiliate or referral programs). Also, please do not promote services that are direct competitors to&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s fine to share your&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu</strong>&nbsp;referral link here and there, but please don&#39;t spam our social media channels by posting your link more than once per day. Chances are, it won&#39;t help you get more referrals, and you&#39;ll just end up annoying <strong>chicsters</strong>&nbsp;who are already subscribed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t post personal information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We value privacy. Please don&#39;t post your own (or another&nbsp;<strong>ipster&#39;s</strong>) phone number, e-mail address, physical mailing address, billing info, or any other personal information. Also, please do not post private correspondence between you and other&nbsp;<strong>ipsters</strong>, or between you and&nbsp;<strong>chiccablu</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t impersonate another ipster.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impersonating another human being is creepy and just plain wrong. Enough said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t use fraudulent trickery to win our contests and giveaways.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This includes creating fake accounts to vote and &quot;like.&quot; We will find out and we will not be happy.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12"><br />\r\n<em>Last updated: April 28, 2015</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2016-07-19 09:08:04', '社区指南', '<div class="row text-left margin-bot"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="padding"><p>欢迎来到Chiccablu网上社区指南，这里有Chiccablu 的网站：Chiccablu.com; 脸书、Twitter 、图片分享、YouTube 及Pinterest</p><p>Chiccablu 不仅仅是美妆产品，它涵盖了世界上各种形式的美。我们推动、鼓励及培养一个传递内在和外之美的社区。我们想要为Chicca的粉丝们创造一个有趣又安全的场所（通过我们的网站、脸书及其他途径）来分享他们的情感爱好，想法、体验及更多其它的内心感受，我们在这里为彼此提供支持并一起学习新的东西，所以请拿出自己最好的姿态！记住：美就是美！</p><p>应该做的</p><p>保持积极乐观</p><p>我们推崇以最积极的方式给与彼此支持，用自己希望被对待的方式对待他人。毫无益处的消极情绪（如咆哮,过度宣泄,刻薄的评论）是无益于增添社区体验的价值的，所以请不要去贬低其它社区成员、Chiccablu设计师、产品、品牌或普通的Chiccablu。</p><p>乐于助人</p><p>我们非常愿意看到社区成员之间彼此互相帮助。经常能看到社区成员之间彼此建议、传授各种秘诀和技巧。这是你们自己的社区，所以我们需要你们的参与，让彼此的沟通变得有趣、睿智、惠及每一个人且能够保持风平浪静。</p><p>分享自己所有</p><p>我们希望能看到你的视频、照片和相貌，我乐于听到你的声音。做好自己，并保持原创！</p><p>直接联系我们</p><p>如果你有任何疑问或建议，最好最快获得回复的方式就是发邮件给&nbsp;<strong>chiccabluCare</strong>.。事实上，鉴于个人隐私，我们不能运用公共论坛来解决许多个人问题。我们会竭尽全力帮助你，回答任何我们所能回答的问题，但是，最好还是先发邮件或者到chiccabluCare 或<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/community-guidelines">tweet @chiccabluCare</a>&nbsp;，这样我们就可以先做调查再帮助你。</p><p>彼此尊重</p><p>我们在此一起发现奥秘、分享知识、一起庆祝我们队所有美好事物的爱。我们彼此之间用优雅和柔和的方式交流非常重要（是的，那是一种承诺！）如果你想要获得别人的尊重，首先要先给与他人尊重。每一个社区成员都有权利通过我们的网站和社会媒体频道参与进来，而不用担心受到嘲笑或贬低（比如，抱怨别人的投诉反而引起了了更多的抱怨!）</p><p>我们这里有来自各行各业的人，所以请注意自己的言辞，避免亵渎之言（有些脏话是不允许说的）：色情方面的及其它任何可能冒犯同社区chicsters的话。</p><p><strong>Chiccablu Stylists</strong>&nbsp;是我们社区一个至关重要的组成部分，且总是非常努力地以惊人的内容激发着我们。请记住，他们也是人，像我们一样，应该受到友善对待和尊重。</p><p>我们有一个针对社区成员的零容忍政策。任何一个针对设计师个人的负面评论、批判、或其它方式的毁谤，我们的设计师作为一个组织，或者一个社区成员同伴，将会被剔除出去。</p><p>请将你的尊重延伸到不仅仅针对chicsters的同伴和chiccablu Stylists，还有chiccabluCare的&nbsp;团队。他们是真正的好人，在这里为你们提供一流的服务和支持，所以对他们好一点。他们一直带着尊重和友善地对待你，所以也请你也这样对待他们。</p><p>不该做的</p><p>请勿粗鲁、残忍或心胸狭隘</p><p>骚扰、恐吓或威胁其他chicsters或诽谤<strong>chiccablu Stylists</strong>、作为一个整体团队，这是一个主要禁忌。</p><p>没有什么比一个用恶意和卑劣的手段去破坏一个好聚会更糟糕的事了。千万别做那种人！</p><p>我们不能容忍谩骂、自私、过于专业、宗教攻击或威胁、种族或性别歧视的言论；讨厌演讲（或任何可以被理解为演讲的言论）；以及其它基于个人外表、种族、种族、宗教、性别、性别认同、残疾、性取向等贬低的言论。</p><p>.请勿散布垃圾</p><p>当你跟你的chicsters同伴分享故事的时候，请提供故事的上下文，不要将同样的内容反复不断地说，不要分享纯粹得商业信息（如加入或推荐项目）。另外，请不要宣扬推进chiccablu竞争对手的服务。</p><p>到处分享你的chiccablu链接是很好的事情，但请每天不要超过一次地在我们的社会媒体渠道上散播你的个人链接。因为这样很有可能不仅不能帮你发展更多的下线，反而会终止已经订阅的chicsters成员。</p><p>请勿发布个人信息</p><p>我们尊重隐私。请勿张贴你个人的（或其它ipster的）电话号码、邮箱地址、邮寄地址、计费信息或其它个人信息。另外，请不要发布你和其他ipsters，或者你和chiccablu之间私人信件。</p><p>请勿冒充他人</p><p>简单地说，冒充另一个人是令人毛骨悚然的、错误的。</p><p>请勿通过欺诈手段赢得竞赛及赠品</p><p>这里包括创建假账户投票及其它类似的事。我们将会发现，并且不会乐意看到这样得事情发生</p></div></div></div>');
INSERT INTO `pages` (`page_id`, `page_title`, `page_content`, `page_updated`, `page_title_ch`, `page_content_ch`) VALUES
(3, 'PRIVACY', '<div class="margin-v text-left">\r\n<p>At chiccablu, you make our world beautiful. We love nothing more than to see our ipster community of members thrive. We know you&#39;re unique, and we know you trust us with your personal information when you visit or join our community. This Privacy Policy spells out our commitment to protect that trust. It explains our privacy practices for&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff3399">chicca-blu.com</span></a>&nbsp;(the &quot;Site&quot;) and services provided by Personalized Beauty Discovery, Inc. (&quot;chiccablu,&quot; &quot;we,&quot; or &quot;us&quot;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in full disclosure when it comes to our privacy practices. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect from you, how we collect it, how we use it and how we protect it. We want you to feel safe in our community, so we use industry-standard safeguards and procedures. We also let you control how much personal information you share and how certain information is used.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By visiting this Site, you accept this Privacy Policy&#39;s terms. You&#39;re not authorized to use this Site unless you agree with this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Privacy Policy applies only to this Site. We&#39;re not responsible for the practices employed by any third-party sites including ones to which we link or that link to us. Those sites will have rules and practices of their own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@chicca-blu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chicca-blu.com</span></a><span style="color:#ff0099">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>INFORMATION COLLECTED OR RECEIVED</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We collect information from you on this Site to provide a meaningful, safe, efficient, and customized experience. We use this information to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>make it easier for you to use this Site,</li>\r\n	<li>communicate with you about your orders, billing and payment,</li>\r\n	<li>verify your identity when you make a purchase on our Site,</li>\r\n	<li>help you more quickly find information on chiccablu&#39;s products and services,</li>\r\n	<li>provide targeted online marketing for the Site,</li>\r\n	<li>create content on this Site that&#39;s more relevant to you, and</li>\r\n	<li>alert you to new products, services and special offers that might specifically interest you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Information You Provide.</strong>\r\n\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li><strong>When You Join chiccablu.</strong>&nbsp;In order to join chiccablu you must complete a beauty quiz that asks for beauty profile information like your skin tone, eye color, hair color, beauty brands and products you love, and where you usually shop for beauty products (your &quot;Beauty Profile&quot;). We use the Beauty Profile information to personalize your experience. If you subscribe to our Glam Bag program then we will use the Beauty Profile information to send you Glam Bag items that fit your unique profile, alerts about chiccablu products, services, and other beauty news that might interest you.</li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">At the end of the beauty quiz, in order to join chiccablu you must choose a username and password. Your username will be visible to other chiccters when they visit the Site, so please choose carefully. You also must provide a valid email address and your date of birth. We use your email to communicate with you about our Site and your registration. We ask for your date of birth to make sure you&#39;re old enough to use our Site and services. And, of course, we also like to wish you a happy birthday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">If you provide us your email address but choose not to become a member, then we will retain your email address for a period to invite you back to the Site.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>When You Order from Us.</strong>&nbsp;If you subscribe to our Glam Bag or order any chiccablu Offer products from us, you must provide your: name, shipping address, billing address, and credit card information.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">We use this information, along with your email, for billing purposes, to fulfill your orders, and to communicate with you about your orders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">We collect your credit card information through our Site. The credit card information is encrypted, and transmitted for storage to a high security vault according to strict industry standards. Once the data reaches the vault it is &quot;tokenized&quot;. No credit card information is retained in chiccablu&#39;s own systems. Instead we retain a token associated with your account that has no intrinsic value. Your credit card information is not exposed anywhere in our own systems. Please do not send your credit card information to our team directly, for example by emailing this information to an chiccabluCare representative. Please use our secure, online system to enter your credit card information.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>When You Request Information from Us.</strong>&nbsp;If you want us to notify you regarding particular products or special offers, including Giveaways, or if you sign up for our emails, you&#39;ll need to give us your email address. We use it to honor your requests, whether that&#39;s emailing you information about certain products or emailing you to tell you about an chiccablu Giveaway.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>When You Post Public Content.</strong>&nbsp;We use this content to bring our community of fabulous chiccsters to life.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong><em>Public information you post on the Site.</em></strong>&nbsp;Information you post publicly on our Site is intended for public consumption. Please be aware that your username and profile image will be publicly displayed. The date you joined chiccablu and some information from your Beauty Profile (such as skin tone, hair color and eye color) will be publicly displayed under your user name, as well as reviews, photos, looks, videos and comments you choose to post. In addition, postings you make on our Site may appear when Internet users execute searches on the subject of your posting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Site visitors may be able to identify you or associate you with your chiccablu account if you include personal information in your account profile or in any content you post. We cannot control who reads your postings or what other users may do with the information you voluntarily post, so we encourage you to exercise discretion and caution with respect to your personal information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">You can reduce the risk of being personally identified by choosing a username and profile image that do not identify you and by taking care to exclude any personal information in your comments, reviews, looks, or videos. You can change your username and profile picture at any time by logging into your account.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Public information you post on other sites. We also may collect information you post publicly on third-party sites, but only if you choose to follow instructions we provide. For example, we may collect pictures you post publicly on wechat and Instagram and re-post them on our Site, but only if you choose to use the hash tag &quot;#chiccablu&quot; inside your Instagram post. You can always have us remove the information from our Site by emailing us using this link:&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a><span style="color:#ff0099">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>When You Share Information about Your Contacts.</strong>&nbsp;You may choose to share personal information about friends, relatives or colleagues with chiccablu, such as the person&#39;s name, shipping address and email address.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">You may choose to manually invite your friends to chiccablu by using the &quot;Invite with Email&quot; button on the Site or by uploading data about your contacts to the Site. You also may grant chiccablu permission to access your contacts list and pull the email addresses of your contacts to invite them to the Site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">If you use the Site to send others an email invitation to become an chiccablu member or subscriber, we may store the personal information of each recipient in order to process those requests or facilitate future activities. All information that you enter or upload about your contacts is covered by the Agreement including our Privacy Policy. We use this information about your friends to enable chiccablu to send invitations and reminders to your friends and to ship products to your friends, if applicable. By providing personal information of others to chiccablu, you represent that you have authority to do so.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>When You Connect to Us with a Third-Party Service.</strong>&nbsp;You can connect to your chiccablu account using external third-party services. The Site collects personal information about you from your social media accounts, but only if you opt-in and permit us to do so. When you connect to us through a third-party service like &nbsp;wechat, QQ, Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus, and Instagram, we receive information from that third party identifying your account. We collect and store this information and use it to help you connect to our Site and to share your public content. Connecting your chiccablu account to a third-party service is completely optional, and you will have the opportunity to grant permission when you attempt to connect. You can revoke permission by logging into the third party service and disconnecting the chiccablu application from there. We may retain the information we collected previously from you.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Information We Automatically Collect or Receive.</strong>\r\n\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li><strong>Log Files.</strong>&nbsp;Like most sites, chiccablu automatically receives and stores in log files certain information from your browser when you visit the Site. This information includes your Internet protocol (&quot;IP&quot;) address, browser type, Internet service provider, the referring/exit pages, your operating system, and the date/time stamp of your Site visit. We use this information, which doesn&#39;t identify individual Site visitors, to analyze and understand how the Site works for you so we can improve it, to administer the Site, and to gather demographic information about Site visitors for targeted online marketing purposes. We may link this automatically collected information to your personal information.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Cookies and Other Tracking Technologies Policy.</strong></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Introduction</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">We use a variety of technologies to help us understand how you use&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">chiccablu.com</span></a>&nbsp;(the &quot;Site&quot;) and our services (collectively, &quot;chiccablu&quot;). This guide explains the tracking technologies chiccablu uses and is part of our commitment to a high standard of transparency in our privacy practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Types of tracking technologies</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Cookies.</strong>&nbsp;This is a small data file sent from a server to your web browser that is stored in your browser and sent back to the server each time the browser makes a request to the server. Cookies can improve a site user&#39;s experience by, for example, allowing the site to keep a user logged in while browsing, saving a user&#39;s site preferences, and allowing a user to add items to a shopping cart and preserve cart contents between site visits, even when the user is not logged in.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Clear gifs, web beacons, tracking pixels.</strong>&nbsp;These are tiny graphics with a unique identifier. They function similarly to cookies and are used to track the online movements of web users. Unlike cookies which are stored on a user&#39;s computer hard drive, clear gifs are embedded on web pages and are single pixel wide. chiccablu does not tie information gathered by clear gifs to your personally identifiable information.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Tracking Technology Lifespans</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Single-session</strong>&nbsp;tracking technology: lasts only as long as your site visit. Single-session cookies expire and delete themselves when you leave the site or close your browser. They are used for technical purposes such as enabling better navigation through a site or generating aggregated statistics about how a site is used. Single-session cookies do not publicly expose your personal information.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Multi-session or persistent</strong>&nbsp;tracking technology: remains on your browser or mobile device until you choose to delete it or the cookie expires. Persistent cookies are used to recognize a computer that has previously visited a site. This can improve the user&#39;s experience, for example by continuing preference settings from previous visits and by allowing users to login without entering a password with every site visit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Tracking Purposes</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">We use tracking technologies for these general purposes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Because it is&nbsp;<strong>strictly necessary</strong>. This tracking is needed to make chiccablu work properly.</li>\r\n	<li>For&nbsp;<strong>performance</strong>. This tracking helps chiccablu understand how the Site is functioning so chiccablu can improve the Site.</li>\r\n	<li>For&nbsp;<strong>functionality</strong>. This tracking retains your personal preferences as you use the Site.</li>\r\n	<li>For&nbsp;<strong>advertising</strong>. This tracking gathers data to help deliver advertising to you that interests you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Cookies chiccablu currently uses</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Single session cookies are used to ensure the Site displays correctly on your device.</li>\r\n	<li>Persistent cookies are used to measure Site metrics such as which pages are popular, how often people visit the Site, whether people are visiting the Site for the first time, and whether visitors make purchases on the Site. They also are used to enhance Site functionality, for example to allow returning users to use the Site without logging in.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Cookies for email subscribers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">We may use cookies to measure the effectiveness of our email communications and to tailor email content. For example, we may connect the data showing that you clicked a link in an email from chiccablu then completed an action on our Site such as buying a Glam Bag. This links cookie data with an individual user, so we only do this for users who have consented and opted in to receiving emails from chiccablu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Third Party Cookies</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">chiccablu partners with third-party service providers who set cookies and tracking pixels for Site visitors and members on our behalf in order to deliver their services. These services include targeted online marketing and analysis of data collected through cookies. These technologies allow a partner to recognize your computer or mobile device each time you visit chiccablu.com or other sites that also utilize the third party&#39;s services, but do not allow access to personally identifiable information from chiccablu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Third parties may choose to include chiccablu widgets on their sites. When you load a site that has chosen to include our widgets, we receive analytics information through a cookie that may be used to enhance our data or to improve our services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">chiccablu does not have access to or control over these third-party technologies, and they are not covered by our Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Managing Cookies</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">You can delete cookies stored in your browser at any time. You also can choose not to accept cookies from any site, including chiccablu.com, by changing the settings of your browser. If you reject or block all cookies in your browser settings, then you will not be able to fully use chiccablu&#39;s services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">chiccablu does not currently act on &quot;do not track&quot; request headers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">For more information about cookies, including how to delete them from your computer and configure the type of browser you use to refuse cookies from any site, visit <a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">GetNetWise</span></a><a href="http://GetNetWise.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><em>Created: February 9, 2015</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Information from other sources.</strong>&nbsp;We may receive information about our users from third party social platforms, such as wechat and Facebook. When you access or use our site or mobile application through such a site, you allow us to access or collect information made available by the third party site in accordance with its privacy policy. This information may be available from your profile or account with the third party site or from cookies placed on your device by the third party site. Depending on your privacy settings this information may include: Facebook interests, gender, friends and location.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Information collected automatically.</strong>&nbsp;We automatically collect information from your browser or device when you visit the Site. This information includes your IP address, device ID, your browser type and language, access times, the content of any undeleted cookies that your browser previously accepted from us, and the referring site address.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Other Information We Receive About You.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">As you might expect, we usually collect or receive information through our Site. But we also may collect information offline, and it&#39;s important to us that we preserve the privacy of your personal information both online and off. For example, if you call us to place an order, we ask for the shipping address needed to place that order. There are other ways we could learn of personal information offline, but this Privacy Policy doesn&#39;t try to predict all those methods. We just want you to know that we try to treat offline information collection, uses, and disclosures consistently with our online privacy practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">If you&#39;re not an chiccablu member but we contacted you, then we may have received your contact information from one of your friends. An chiccablu member may give us your name and email address so chiccablu can send a personalized invitation to you to join chiccablu. We also may send you personalized email &lsquo;reminders&#39; about chiccablu from your friends. Similarly, an chiccablu member may provide your personal information to us so we can ship a gift or other merchandise to you. We ask your contacts to share your personal information only with your permission.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>HOW WE MAY DISCLOSE THE INFORMATION WE COLLECT OR RECEIVE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">Information we collect from you may be either personal or aggregate. Personal information is identifiable to you, like your name, email address, shipping and billing addresses, credit card information, and phone number. Aggregate information is summary data of the behaviors and interests of groups or categories, so it won&#39;t identify you.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Aggregate Information.</strong>&nbsp;We use aggregate information for the purposes of internal business research, sales and business development and reporting back to our brand partners. We may share aggregated information about our visitor and user base with third parties such as our advertising partners. This information may include the number of daily visitors to our Site and the number of orders placed on a certain date. We also may share Beauty Profile information with brand partners. We do not link aggregated data with our ipsters&#39; personal information.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Personal Information.</strong>&nbsp;We do not sell, rent, trade, license, or otherwise disclose your personal information to third parties, except in these limited circumstances:\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li><strong>Disclosures to chiccablu Agents, Consultants and Related Third Parties.</strong>&nbsp;Like most Internet retailers, we use third parties to help ensure our business runs smoothly. We disclose your information to these third-party companies so they can perform their specific functions for us. For example, we may provide your name, shipping address, email and phone number to third-party shippers like the U.S. Postal Service and the United Parcel Service to deliver our products to you. We also may provide your credit card information to third-party credit card processors and issuers to help us process your orders from us. When we employ other companies to perform functions of this nature, we only disclose the information that they need to perform their requested function. We do not authorize them to retain, share, store, or use personal information provided by us for any other purpose.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Disclosures Required by Law or Otherwise.</strong>&nbsp;We may disclose your personal information if we believe, in good faith, that it&#39;s necessary to: (1) comply with a legal obligation such as in response to a court order or subpoena; (2) protect the safety of fellow ipsters or the public; (3) protect against legal liability; or (4) protect and defend chiccablu&#39;s rights or property.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Disclosures for a Business Transaction or Insolvency.</strong>&nbsp;We also may disclose your personal information in connection with an actual or proposed corporate transaction or insolvency proceeding involving all or part of chiccablu&#39;s business or assets. For example, if we merge with another company, we may disclose your personal information to that company, but the disclosure would be subject to our Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Disclosures of Giveaway Winners.</strong>&nbsp;We post the chiccablu user names or social media handles of our lucky Giveaway winners on our wechat and Facebook page.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Disclosures through Social Media.</strong>&nbsp;Remember that you control the privacy settings on each of your social media platforms. We allow you to share information from the Site to social media. In order for this to happen you first must opt-in. You can revoke permission to do this by logging into the social media service and disconnecting the chiccablu application from there.</li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HOW YOU CAN CONTROL YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Log Into Your Account.</strong>&nbsp;You can change the personal information you provide to us and remove any content you post publicly on our Site, including reviews, looks and videos, by logging into your chiccablu account and making the appropriate changes.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Contact Us.</strong>&nbsp;You can request that we take down any of your personal content on the Site by emailing us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a>. We will remove your public posts from view, but we may retain personal information about you solely for the purposes authorized under this Privacy Policy. For example, we may retain information to prevent, investigate, or identify possible wrongdoing in connection with the Site or to comply with legal obligations.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Opt-Out.</strong>&nbsp;You can always &quot;opt-out&quot; of having your personal information used for certain purposes. At your request, we will stop sending you certain emails or even deactivate your account to prevent any future purchases through it. You can submit these requests at any time by emailing us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Block Cookies and Targeted Advertising.</strong>&nbsp;You can prevent chiccablu and its third-party partners from setting and accessing cookies on your computer by setting your Internet browser to block cookies. You also may remove yourself from the targeted advertising of companies participating in the Digital Advertising Alliance program by opting out here: <a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">aboutads.info/choices/</span></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">Our Site does not act on &quot;do not track&quot; request headers, but you can still limit tracking by taking these steps.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Cancel Your Subscription or Deactivate Your Account.</strong>&nbsp;You may cancel your Glam Bag subscription by logging into your account, clicking on &quot;My Account&quot; and choosing &quot;cancel subscription&quot; under &quot;Subscription Details.&quot; You may deactivate your chiccablu account by emailing us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a>&nbsp;with the subject line: &quot;Account Deactivation Request.&quot;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HOW WE PROTECT YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At chiccablu, we take data security seriously. We use technical, physical and administrative safeguards. Online, we encrypt your personal information using Secure Sockets Layer (&quot;SSL&quot;). SSL allows for a private, reliable Site connection where your identity is authenticated with cryptography. Offline, we restrict access to your personal information to only those chiccablu employees who need it to perform a specific job function. And we require all chiccablu employees with access to your personal information to follow specific practices concerning its proper handling. We also hold our vendors who need access to your personal information to strict confidentiality requirements. Third-party service providers assist us with the physical security of some of our computer hardware. When you visit our Site, you access servers that we backup constantly. Our servers are hosted at locations which are private and secure data center facilities, behind physical and virtual firewalls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But please remember, while we use industry-standard precautions to safeguard your personal information, we can&#39;t guarantee absolute security. We wish we could, but 100% security just doesn&#39;t exist anywhere online or off.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CHILDREN&#39;S PRIVACY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We respect children&#39;s privacy. This Site is not intended for persons under the age of 13 (see chiccablu&#39;s Terms of Use). If you&#39;re under 18 years old, please do not submit any personal information to us without the consent and supervision of a responsible parent or legal guardian.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DATA RETENTION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>chiccablu will retain your information as long as we deem necessary. If you no longer want chiccablu to use your information to provide you Services, you may close your account. If you close your account then your profile and the content you posted to the Site will no longer appear on the Site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may inform us of any changes or requests in regards to your personal data, and in accordance with our obligations under local data protection law, we will use all reasonable means to update or delete your personal data accordingly. Please email chiccabluCare using this link:&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>. You should not expect that all of your information will be completely removed from our databases in response to your request. chiccablu will retain and use your information as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes and enforce our agreements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>UPDATES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will post any changes and updates to this Privacy Policy on this Site so you can always be aware of what information we collect, use and disclose. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically so you&#39;ll know if it has been changed or updated.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2016-07-19 09:09:53', '隐私权', '<p>在chiccablu社区，是你让我们的世界变得更加美好。没有什么能比看到我们的社区成员的茁壮成长更加快乐的事了。当你访问并加入我们的社区时，我们知道你是唯一的，我们也知道你是信任我们才会把个人信息都告诉我们。这个隐私权政策就是我们为了保护你对我们的这份信任而作出的承诺。以下网址：&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">chicca-blu.com</span></a>详细描述了隐私权政策的内容以及发现个性之美有限公司（包括文中所指的&ldquo;chiccablu&rdquo;、&ldquo;我们&rdquo;）提供的所有服务。</p><p>我们详细阐述了隐私权政策的相关内容。隐私权政策就是关于从你身上收集的个人信息，包括如何收集、如何使用以及如何保护它们。我们希望你们能在我们的社区获得安全感，所以我们运用行业标准的保障措施和程序来保障。我们会让你们自己把握和分享开放个人信息量以及了解部分信息是如何被使用的。</p><p>当你登录本站点的同时就意味着你接受本隐私权政策的相关条款。如不能接受，你将无权使用本网站。</p><p>此隐私权政策仅适用于本网站。任何实际接入的第三方站点，包括我们链接的或者其它网站链接的本网站，均与此隐私权政策无关，我们概不负责隐私权的保护；这些站点有他们自己的保护条例和措施。</p><p>如有任何问题或者想了解更多有关隐私权政策的内容，请按以下网址发邮件给我们：<a href="mailto:privacy@chicca-blu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chicca-blu.com</span></a></p><p><strong>信息的收集或接收</strong></p><p>我们从网站上收集你的个人信息以提供一种有意义的、安全的、有效的、定制化的体验。我们收集的信息主要有以下用途：</p><ul>	<li>让你更方便地使用本网站</li>	<li>方便在你订购产品、确认账单和付款时与我们沟通</li>	<li>在网站购物时确认身份信息</li>	<li>帮助你更加快速地找到产品和服务信息</li>	<li>提供有针对性的市场网站</li>	<li>创造更满意的购物体验</li>	<li>为你推荐特别感兴趣的新产品、服务和特价优惠信息</li></ul><ol>	<li><strong>你需要提供的信息</strong>	<ol>		<li><strong>加入</strong><strong>chiccablu</strong><strong>时</strong>：要想加入chiccablu，你必须先完成一个美容测试，我们会咨询有关你的美容概况，如肤色、眼睛颜色、头发颜色、喜欢的美容品牌和产品，以及经常光顾的美容商店有哪些（这些信息统称&ldquo;美容概况&rdquo;）。我们会将你的美容概况融入你的个性化体验中。如果你订购了我们的魅力袋产品，我们会根据的美容概况为你量身定制魅力袋的产品内容，推荐chiccablu的相关产品和服务以及其它让你感兴趣的资讯。</li>	</ol>	</li></ol><p style="margin-left: 80px;">美容测试之后，你还要选择一个用户名和密码。当你登录网站时，所有的会员都能看到你的用户 名，所以请慎重选择。你还需要提供一个有效的电子邮箱账号以及出生日期。我们会以邮件的方式与你沟通有关网站和注册的事宜。我们询问你的出生日期是为了确 保你已符合年龄要求来使用本网站的产品和服务。当然，我们也会在生日时祝你生日快乐。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">如果你提供了电子邮箱给我们但不注册会员，我们也会保留你的邮箱地址并在适当的时候邀请你重新加入我们。</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 订购产品时</strong>：当你订购了我们的魅力袋或者任何其它的产品，你需提供姓名、收件地址、账单地址以及信用卡信息。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">我们使用这些信息，还有电子邮箱信息，来填写你的订单、账单，以及与你沟通涉及订单的事宜。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">我们通过网站来收集你的信用卡信息，这些信息都是经过加密处理的，信息的传送也是按照高度安全、严格的工业标准来保障的。信用卡信息不会被保留在chiccablu自己的系统上，我们只保留与你账户关联的无内在价值的口令信息。你的信用卡信息不会在我们的系统上泄露出去，请勿将信息直接发送给我们的团队成员，例如通过邮件将信息发送给一个代理人。请使用我们安全的在线系统来填写信用卡信息。</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. 获取我们的信息：</strong>如果你需要我们通知你有关特别的产品、特价的优惠，包括随赠品等信息，你只需将电子邮箱地址发给我们。我们很重视你的请求，会将相关产品的信息发送给你或者告诉你有可以领&nbsp; 取的赠品消息。</p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. 公开个人信息：</strong>我们公开这些信息的目的是为了让我们社区成员的生活变得更加美好。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;"><strong><em>网站公开显示的信息：</em></strong>你在我们网站上发布的信息是面向公共群体的。你的用户名和基本信息将会公开显示出来。你加入社区的时间和一些美容概况（例如肤色、头发颜色、眼睛颜色）将会公开显示在你的用户名之下，还有你发布并选择公开的评论、照片、相貌、视频文件等也将公开显示。另外，你在我们网站上发布的内容也会被别的互联网用户通过搜索引擎搜索到。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">网站的访问者会通过你的账户信息或者你发布出来的信息来认识你，或者和你交朋友。我们无法控制哪些人浏览你发布的内容，更无法控制别的访问者会用你自愿发布的信息作何用途，所以我们建议你谨慎处理这些个人信息。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">你可以通过选择用户名和使用不暴露自己真实相貌的头像，谨慎发布含有个人信息的评论、照片或视频来降低个人信息泄露的风险。你还可以随时更改用户名和头像。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">你在其它网站公开的信息。我们也可以通过第三方网站来收集你的个人信息，但仅当你按照我们的操作说明进行操作时才能进行。比如，我们可以从你发布在微信和Instagram上的照片转载到我们的网站上，但仅当你使用Instagram上的照片转载到我们的网站上，但仅当你使用Instagram上内置的&quot;#chiccablu&quot;控件进行转载操作时才会转载。你可以通过以下链接发邮件给我们删除已发布的信息：&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt">&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. 分享个人信息：</strong>你可以和chiccablu上的其它成员分享关于你朋友、亲属和同事等的信息，以及你的真实姓名、收件地址和电子邮箱等信息。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">你可以通过点击&ldquo;Invite with Email&rdquo;（邮箱邀请）按钮手动邀请你的朋友加入chiccablu，或者将通讯录上传至网站，同时你同意chiccablu访问和接入你的通讯录并通过邮箱地址向通讯录中的名单发送邀请。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">如果你通过本站点向其它人发送邀请，让他们也成为chiccablu成员并注册用户，我们会储存每一个接受邀请者的个人信息以处理这些请求或促进未来更多的活动。你接入或上传的所有通讯录信息都会受到包括隐私权政策在内的相关协议的保护。我们使用你朋友的这些信息以通过chiccablu发送邀请，甚至发送产品，如果许可的话。你有权管理和决定是否提供其它人的个人信息给chiccablu.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 6. 通过第三方服务联系我们：</strong>你可以用你的账户通过第三方服务联系我们。本网站可以从你的社交媒体账户上收集你的个人信息，但首先要获得你的授权。当你通过微信、QQ、 Facebook、Twitter、&nbsp; Google Plus和 Instagram等第三方服务来联系我们时，我们会通过第三方服务器来验证你的账户。我们收集并储存这些信息以便于帮助你连接我们的网站来分享你公开的信息。要想将你的chiccablu账户和第三方服务器连接，首先要获得你的准许授权。你可以登录进入第三方服务器来断开与chiccablu的连接，我们会保留之前储存的信息。</p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 自动收集和接收信息</strong></p><ol style="margin-left: 40px;">	<li><strong>记录文件：</strong>和其它大多数的网站一样，chiccablu会自动接收和储存你登录网站后的一些浏览记录等文件。这些文件包括你的IP地址、浏览方式、网络服务商、引用/退出页面、你的操作系统、以及浏览时间。我们使用这些无法识别个人站点访问者的信息赖分析和推断我们的网站是如何为你服务以进一步改进它、管理它、并根据站点访问者的统计信息来达到定向网络营销的目的。我们可能根据链接来自动收集你的个人信息。</li>	<li><strong>Cookies</strong><strong>（缓存的小型文本文件</strong><strong>）和其它跟踪技术政策</strong></li></ol><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>简介</strong></p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">我们利用多种技术手段来帮助我们了解你如何使用我们的网站（<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">chiccablu.com</span></a>）和服务（&quot;chiccablu&quot;）。此指南将解释我们的跟踪技术是如何运用的，并且是我们对践行隐私权政策的一项高度透明的承诺。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>跟踪技术方式</strong></p><ul style="margin-left: 80px;">	<li><strong>Cookies</strong><strong>：</strong>这是从服务器中向你的浏览器发送的一个很小的数据，它储存在你的浏览器中，当你每次从浏览器发出登录请求的时候，就会将这些储存的数据发回给服务器。Cookies能更好地提升网站使用者的体验，例如，可以保存用户登录信息、保存用户的偏好设置、添加商品到购物车并在不同网页跳转时保留购物车里的信息，甚至在未登录账户时有可以保留。</li>	<li><strong>图标、网站指引、跟踪像素：</strong>有一些带有独特标识符的图像，他们类似于Cookies那样运行，可以用来跟踪访问者的使用轨迹。不同于Cookies的是，它存储在用户电脑硬盘上，嵌入网站页面的图标都是单像素的，chiccablu不会收集这些单像素图标来识别你的个人信息。</li></ul><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>跟踪技术期限</strong></p><ul style="margin-left: 80px;">	<li><strong>单程会话跟踪技术：</strong>单程会话的Cookies只会在你访问网站时保存，当你离开网站或者关闭浏览器之后会失效和自动删除。他们主要用于技术目的，例如授权浏览站点或者收集统计此站点被使用的数据。单程会话文件不会公开在你的个人信息上。</li>	<li><strong>多重区段或持续跟踪技术：</strong>除非你选择删除或者文件到期，否则将一直留存在你浏览器或移动设备上。固定文件被用来识别你之前已经登录过的电脑。这个能提升用户体验，比如连续优先选定之前登录过的用户以及免除用户访问站点时输入密码的繁琐。</li></ul><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>跟踪目的</strong></p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">我们运用跟踪技术主要用于以下这些目的：</p><ul style="margin-left: 80px;">	<li>因为<strong>很有必要。</strong>跟踪技术是保证chiccablu正常运行的必要条件。</li>	<li>为了<strong>提升性能</strong>。跟踪技术可以帮助我们了解chiccablu的运行状态，以更好地提升网站性能。</li>	<li>为了<strong>增添功能</strong>。跟踪技术可以保存个人偏好设置。</li>	<li>为了<strong>发布广告</strong>。跟踪技术可以收据数据，帮助发送一些你感兴趣的广告信息给你。</li></ul><p style="margin-left:96.75pt">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Cookies</strong><strong>的一般应用</strong></p><ul style="margin-left: 80px;">	<li>单会话Cookies的应用目的是为了确保网站能在你的设备上正确地显示。</li>	<li>固定Cookies的使用目的是为了监测网站的运行，比如网页是否受欢迎，人们每隔多久会访问，是否初次访问，以及是否在网站订购产品。同时也为了完善网站功能，例如再次登录时可以免除重新输入用户名和密码的繁琐。</li></ul><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Cookies</strong><strong>应用于邮件订购</strong></p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">我们可以运用Cookies使我们邮件沟通变得更有效率并且可以截取部分邮件内容。例如，当我们点击一封发自chiccablu的邮件上的一个连接之后，即可在这个网站上完成例如订购魅力袋之类的操作。这个链接缓存数据仅与个人用户关联，所以我们仅针对同意并选择接收chiccablu邮箱的用户使用。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>第三方</strong><strong>Cookies</strong></p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">提供第三方服务的chiccablu合作伙伴，和代表我们方的其它组织，对本站点的访问者设置Cookies和像素追踪的目的都是为了更好地推送他们的服务。这些服务包括针对性地网络营销和数据分析。这些技术允许合作伙伴当你每次登陆chiccablu.com或其它运用了第三方服务的网站时都能识别出你的计算机或移动终端，但是不会允许从chiccablu网站上访问你的个人信息。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">第三方合作伙伴会在它们的网站中使用包含chiccablu的小插件。当你登录网站并选择加载这个小插件时，我们就会通过缓存文件接收分析信息以用于增强我们的数据并改善我们的服务。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Chiccablu无权利用和控制这些第三方插件技术，这些技术不适用于本隐私权政策。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Managing Cooki</strong><strong>es</strong> <strong>Cookies</strong><strong>管理</strong></p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">你可以随时从浏览器中删除这些Cookies文件。你也可以通过设置浏览器，选择不接受包括chiccablu.com在内的任何网站的Cookies文件。如果你在浏览器设置中拒绝或阻挡了Cookies文件，你将不能充分享受chiccablu服务。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Chiccablu一般不会在&ldquo;请勿追踪&rdquo;上扮演首当其冲的角色。</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt">想要获取更多有关Cookies文件的信息，包括如何从电脑中删除和如何设置浏览器以阻挡任何网页的Cookies，可以点击以下链接：<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">GetNetWise</span></a>.com</p><p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><em>创建于：</em><em>2015</em><em>年</em><em>2</em><em>月</em><em>9</em><em>日</em></p><p style="margin-left: 80px;"><strong>3. 其它来源信息：</strong>我们可以从第三方社交平台上获取用户信息，例如微信和Facebook。当你登录进入我们的网站或从移动应用程序中进入网站时，你允许我们访问和收集符合第三方隐私权政策的可利用的信息。这些信息可能是你在第三方网站上的用户资料和账号或者是第三方网站留存在你设备中的缓存文件。取决于你的隐私设置，这些信息可能包括你的兴趣爱好、性别、朋友圈和位置信息。</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;"><strong>4. 自动信息收集：</strong>当你登录网站时，我们会自动收集你浏览器或设备上的信息。这些信息包括IP地址、设备编码、浏览器类型和语言、访问时间、你的浏览器之前从我们的网站接收且未被删除的缓存文件、以及网站地址。</p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. 我们收集的其它信息</strong></p><p style="margin-left:24.75pt">如你所料，我们经常从线上收集和接收信息，但我们也可以从线下收集信息，无论线上还是线下收集的信息，保护好个人隐私都至关重要。比如，你打电话过来订购，我们会询问你需要用来发货的快递地址。还有很多其它的线下信息收集方式，但本隐私权政策无法涵盖所有的收集方式。我们只是想让你知悉，我们会尽力做到对待线下信息的收集、使用或公开，跟线上收集一样地保护你的隐私权。</p><p style="margin-left:24.75pt">如果你还不是chiccablu成员，但我们有人联系你，那可能是你的朋友之一是我们的成员。Chiccablu的成员给了我们你的名字和电子邮箱信息，所以我们能将个性化的邀请发给你以让你加入我们。我们同样会发送另一封发自你朋友的个性化的&ldquo;提醒&rdquo;邮件。类似如此，其中一个chiccablu成员给了我们你的个人信息，我们才能发送礼物或者其它商品给你。只有通过你许可分享个人信息之后，我们才能询问你的联系人。</p><p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>我们如何公开收集和接收到的信息</strong></p><p style="margin-left:24.75pt">我们从你身上收集的信息包括个人信息和群体信息。个人信息是用来识别你个人的，例如名字、电子邮箱、快递和账单地址、信用卡信息以及手机号码。群体信息是一个群体或类别的行为和兴趣爱好的汇总数据，所有不会用来识别个人。</p><ol style="margin-left: 40px;">	<li><strong>群体信息：</strong>我们运用群体信息来进行互联网商业研究，销售产品、商业开发、品牌合作伙伴的信息反馈等。我们可能会跟我们的第三方合作伙伴如广告合作商共同分享网站访问者和用户的群体信息。这些信息可能包括每日访问量和某些日期的订单量。我们也会跟我们的品牌合作伙伴分享美容测试信息，但我们不会分享我们注册用户的个人信息数据。</li>	<li><strong>个人信息：</strong>我们不会销售、出租、交易、许可或以其它方式将你的个人信息公开给第三方合作伙伴，除了以下这些有限情况：	<ol>		<li><strong>公开给</strong><strong>chiccablu</strong><strong>代理、咨询公司或相关第三方合作伙伴：</strong>跟大多数互联网企业一样，我们使用第三方合作伙伴以确保我们的商业活动能平稳运行。我们将你的个人信息公开给这些第三方公司以方便他们提供特殊功能给我们。比如，我们会将你的姓名、收件地址、电子邮箱和手机号码提供给美国邮政局和美国联合包裹服务公司等物流公司，以便将我们的产品运送给你。我们还会将你的信用卡信息提供给第三方信用卡处理器和发行者以帮助我们下订单。当我们雇佣其它公司来执行这些功能时，我们仅会公开他们需要用来完成这些功能的信息。我们不会授权他们保留、分享、储存或将个人信息提供给任何其它机构。</li>		<li><strong>因法律方面或其它方面需要的公开：</strong>我们有理由相信以下这些情况公开你的个人信息是完全有必要的：（1）依照相关法律法规的规定公开，例如执行法院命令或传票；（2）保障其它用户或者公众的安全；（3）保障法律责任；（4）以及保障chiccablu成员的权益和财产安全。</li>		<li><strong>因商业贸易或公司破产而公开：</strong>我们可能会因现行的一些商业事务或者执行破产程序而公开部分与chiccablu成员有关的商业和财产信息。例如，如果我们与其它公司合并，我们会将你的个人信息公开给另一家公司，但公开的内容同样会收到隐私权政策的保护。</li>		<li><strong>奖品获得者的公开：</strong>我们会把奖品获得者的用户名公开在微信、Facebook等社交媒体的页面上。</li>		<li><strong>通过社会媒体公开：</strong>请记住你拥有对任何社会媒体平台上的隐私权设置的掌控权。我们允许你将个人信息从这个网站分享到其它社会媒体上。你可以选择性分享，你也可以通过登录账户并且终止这些社会媒体与chiccablu的连接申请来撤销许可分享。</li>	</ol>	</li></ol><p><strong>如何管理个人信息</strong></p><ol>	<li><strong>登录账号：</strong>你可以登录账户来更改个人信息，删除任何你公开在网站上的信息，包括评论、照片和视频。</li>	<li><strong>联系我们：</strong>你可以通过以下网址：<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a>发送邮件给我们，要求我们删除网站上你个人的任何内容。我们将删除你在网站上相应的信息，但会保留隐私权政策规定的部分个人信息。例如，我们会保留部分信息以防止、调查、鉴别与网站关联的可能发生的犯罪行为或者履行某些法律义务的需要。</li>	<li><strong>选择退出：</strong>你可以随时因为某些目的而选择退出，我们将不再发送电子邮件给你或者使你的账户失效而防止通过它来购买任何产品。你随时可以通过以下地址发送邮件给我们来提交这些申请：<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a><strong>.</strong></li>	<li><strong>封锁</strong><strong>Cookie</strong><strong>和针对性广告：</strong>你可以通过设置浏览器来阻挡chiccablu 和它的第三方合作伙伴对Cookie文件的设置和访问来达到封锁Cookie的目的。您也可以通过以下网址退出，删除自己参与的定向广告公司提供的数字广告联盟计划：<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">aboutads.info/choices/</span></a><strong>.</strong></li></ol><p style="margin-left: 40px;">我们的网站不会采取 &ldquo;不追踪&rdquo;请求的行动，但是你仍然可以通过这些步骤来实现限制追踪。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. <strong>取消订购或停用账户：</strong>你可以通过登录账户取消魅力袋的订购，点击&ldquo;我的账户&rdquo;并仔细阅读订购说明后选择&ldquo;取消订购&rdquo;。你也可以通过&ldquo;账号停用请求&rdquo;标题下的<a href="mailto:privacy@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">privacy@chiccablu.com</span></a>&nbsp;链接发送邮件给我们来停用账户。</p><p><strong>我们如何保护你的个人信息安全</strong></p><p>我们很重视数据安全。我们运用技术的、物理的及行政的手段来保障它的安全性。在线上，我们运用SSL技术将你的个人信息编译成密码。SSL是一种可靠的网站连接技术，通过认证密码来识别你的个人信息。在线下，我们限制访问你的个人信息，只有chiccablu员工为了达到特殊的功能需求才能访问。我们要求所有chiccablu员工访问您的个人信息时必须遵循特定的实践条例。我们也要求我们的供应商需要访问您的个人信息时执行严格的保密措施。第三方服务商为我们的一些计算机硬件的物理安全提供帮助。当你登录我们的网站时，你访问的服务器会不断地进行备份。我们的服务器托管在物理和虚拟防火墙的后面、安全可靠的数据库中心设施上。但是，虽然我们采用了行业标准的措施来保障你的个人信息安全，但也并不是意味着会绝对安全；我们希望可以绝对保障安全，但100%的安全保障无论是线上还是线下都是不可能实现的。</p><p><strong>儿童隐私权</strong></p><p>我们尊重儿童的隐私。本网站禁止对13岁以下人员开放（请查阅chiccablu条款使用条例）。如果你未满18岁，请勿在未取得父母或者法定监护人的同意下提交任何你的个人信息给我们。</p><p><strong>数据保存</strong></p><p>如果我们认为有必要，会保留你的部分信息。如你不再希望我们运用你的信息提供服务给你，你可以关闭你的账户。如果你关闭了账户，你的简介以及在网站上发布的内容都将不再显示。你可以将有关于你个人数据的任何变更或者请求告诉我们，按照当地个人数据保护法的有关规定，我们将会采用所有合理的方式来更新或者删除你的个人信息。请通过以下链接联系我们：&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/privacy" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>.你也不会希望看到，在你的要求下，你所有的个人信息都从我们的数据库中删除。我们会根据相关法律义务，为了解决争端和执行我们的协议保留你必要的部分个人信息。</p><p><strong>隐私权政策的更新</strong></p><p>我们会将任何有关隐私权的更新内容发布到本网站，以便让你了解我们对信息的收集、使用和公开的政策。我们建议你定期关注隐私权政策内容，以便了解它的最新动态。</p><p>&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `pages` (`page_id`, `page_title`, `page_content`, `page_updated`, `page_title_ch`, `page_content_ch`) VALUES
(4, 'COPYRIGHT AND INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY', '<p>Shenzhen Pegasus Tec Info LTD (&ldquo;SPTI&rdquo;) has adopted the following general policy toward copyright and intellectual property infringement in accordance with general U.S.and intellectual property laws and the Digital Millennium Copyright Act. SPTI will respond to notices of this form from jurisdictions other than the U.S. as well. The address of SPTI&#39;s Designated Agent to Receive Notification of Claimed Infringement (&quot;Designated Agent&quot;) is listed at the end of this policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SPTI may act expeditiously to respond to a proper notice by removing or disabling access to material claimed to be subject of infringing activity. If SPTI removes or disables access to material in response to such a notice, SPTI will make a good-faith attempt to contact the allegedly infringing party who provided the material to SPTI (&quot;Member&quot;) so that the party may make a counter notification.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A. Procedure for Reporting Copyright or Intellectual Property Infringements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you materially misrepresent that a product or activity is infringing your intellectual property, you may be liable for damages (including costs and attorneys&#39; fees). Therefore, if you are not sure whether the material infringes upon your intellectual property, please contact an attorney before contacting SPTI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe that material residing on or accessible through the SPTI web site&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/copyright-and-intellectual-property" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chicca-blu.com</span></a>&nbsp;(the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;) infringes a copyright or other intellectual property right then you may notify SPTI. To provide SPTI notice of such infringement, you may send a notice of infringement to the Designated Agent listed below (preferably via email to&nbsp;<a href="mailto:legal@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">legal@chicca-blu.com</span></a>). The notice must specify the type of infringement at issue and must include the following information:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A signature of a person authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the copyright or intellectual property right that has been allegedly infringed upon (signatures may be provided electronically by typing your name);</li>\r\n	<li>Identification in sufficient detail of the material being infringed upon (for an allegation of a patent infringement, please provide a patent number);</li>\r\n	<li>Identification of the material on the SPTI Site that is claimed to be infringing upon the intellectual property. Include information regarding the location of the infringing material with sufficient detail so that SPTI is capable of finding and verifying its existence;</li>\r\n	<li>Contact information about the notifier including the name of the intellectual property owner, the name and title of the person contacting SPTI on the owner&#39;s behalf, the address, telephone number and email address;</li>\r\n	<li>A statement that the notifier has a good faith belief that the material is not authorized by the intellectual property or copyright owner, its agent, or the law; and</li>\r\n	<li>A statement made under penalty of perjury that the information provided is accurate and the notifying party is authorized to make the complaint on behalf of the intellectual property or copyright owner.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>When removing material from the Site, SPTI will make reasonable attempts to inform the Member of the removal, the reason for the removal, and may provide the Member with a copy of the notice and the notifying party&rsquo;s contact information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B. Removal of Allegedly Infringing Material</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once Proper Bona Fide Infringement Notification is received by the Designated Agent, SPTI may remove or disable access to the material infringing upon the intellectual property. If SPTI removes or disables access to content in response to an infringement notice, SPTI will make reasonable attempts to notify the Member that SPTI has removed or disabled access to the material. Repeat offenders will have all material they have provided to SPTI removed from the Site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C. Procedure to Supply a Copyright Counter-Notice to the Designated Agent</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you materially misrepresent that a product or activity is not infringing upon the intellectual property, you may be liable for damages (including costs and attorneys&rsquo; fees). Therefore, if you are not sure whether or not the material infringes on the intellectual property, please contact an attorney before contacting SPTI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If a Member believes that their material that was removed or to which access was disabled is not infringing upon a copyright, then the Member may send a counter-notice, pursuant to 512(g)(2) and (3) of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act. The counter-notice must contain the following information to the Designated Agent listed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Your signature (signatures may be provided electronically by typing your name);</li>\r\n	<li>Identification of the material that has been removed or to which access has been disabled and the location at which the material appeared before it was removed or disabled;</li>\r\n	<li>A statement, under penalty of perjury, that you have a good faith belief that the material was removed or disabled as a result of mistake or misidentification of the material;</li>\r\n	<li>Your name, address, telephone number, and email address, and a statement that you consent to the jurisdiction of the Federal Court for the judicial district in which the your address is located, or if your address is located outside the United States, for any judicial district in which SPTI is located, and that you will accept service of process from the person who provided notification under subsection (c)(1)(C) of 17 U.S.C. 512, or an agent of such person.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If a counter-notice is received by the Designated Agent, SPTI may send a copy of the counter-notice to the original complaining party informing that person that SPTI may replace the removed material or cease disabling it in 10 business days. Unless the copyright or intellectual property owner files an action seeking a court order against the Member, the removed material may be replaced or access to it restored in 10 to 14 business days after receipt of the counter-notice, at SPTI&rsquo;s discretion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please contact SPTI&rsquo;s Designated Agent to submit Notifications of Claimed Infringement and Copyright Counter-Notices by email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:legal@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">legal@chicca-blu.com</span></a>&nbsp;(preferred), or at the following address:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designated Agent to Receive Notification of Claimed Infringement:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information on copyright law visit&nbsp;<a href="http://www.copyright.gov/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.copyright.gov</span></a>. For more information on patent and trademark law visit&nbsp;<a href="http://www.uspto.gov/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.uspto.gov</span></a>. Please consult a licensed attorney for specific questions.</p>\r\n', '2016-07-19 09:10:11', '版权和知识产权', '<p>深圳市佩格索斯科技信息有限公司（&ldquo;SPTI&rdquo;）已通过了以下的版权和知识产权侵权的常规政策，其依据了通用的美国及知识产权法律和《数字千年版权法案》。SPTI将以这种模式推广到美国之外的其它地区。SPTI公司用于接收侵权通知的地址（指定代理）标示于本政策的结尾处。</p><p>SPTI可能会通过删除或禁用访问材料的方式以迅速回击各种侵权活动。如果SPTI以删除或禁止访问材料的方式迅速回击此类侵权活动，SPTI将会有诚意的尝试联系向SPTI提供材料的涉嫌侵权的一方（&ldquo;会员&rdquo;），以便当事人提出抗辩通知。</p><p><strong>A</strong><strong>．版权程序报告或知识产权侵权行为</strong></p><p>如果您有严重歪曲产品或侵犯知识产权的活动，您可能会承担损害赔偿责任（包括成本和律师费用）。因此，如果您不太确定您的材料是否侵犯了知识产权，请在联系SPTI公司之前先与律师联系。</p><p>如果您认为通过SPTI网站<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/copyright-and-intellectual-property" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chicca-blu.com</span></a>（以下简称&ldquo;网站&rdquo;）得到或获取的材料，侵犯了版权或其他知识产权的权利，那么您可以通知SPTI。要提供此类侵权通知，您可以先发送一个侵权通知给SPTI公司下面列出的指定代理机构（最好发送至此邮箱：&nbsp;<a href="mailto:legal@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">legal@chicca-blu.com</span></a>）。该通知必须指出有争议的侵权类型，并且必须包括以下信息：</p><ol>	<li>一个版权所有者授权代表的签名或已经涉嫌侵犯的知识产权（签名可以以电子方式即电子签名的方式提供）</li>	<li>足够详细的被侵犯的鉴定材料（侵犯专利权的，请提供专利号）</li>	<li>SPTI网站上出现的声称是侵犯知识产权的识别材料，包括足够细节的侵犯材料位置信息，这样SPTI公司才能够发现并验证它的存在。</li>	<li>接收的侵权通知应包括知识产权所有者的名字、联系SPTI的代表的头衔和名字、地址、电话及电子邮箱。</li>	<li>一份关于此通知的声明，声明中指出发出通知者有充分的理由相信，该材料未经知识产权，或版权拥有者，其代理人或法律授权；</li>	<li>一份有关做伪证的惩罚的声明，声明中指出所提供的信息是准确的，且发出通知一方向已授权代表知识产权或版权拥有者作出投诉。</li></ol><p style="margin-left:24.75pt">一旦材料从网站上删除，SPTI公司将会采取行动尝试通知删除的成员，告知删除的原因，并且向该成员提供此侵权通知的复件和提交侵权通知人的联系方式。</p><p><strong>B</strong><strong>．删除涉嫌侵权的材料</strong></p><p>指定的代理一旦接收到善意且恰当的侵权通知，基于知识产权，SPTI可能会删除或禁止访问侵权材料。如果SPTI公司以删除或禁用访问内容的方式回应该侵权通知，SPTI还将尝试以合理的方式通知相关产权所有者我们已经将材料删除或禁止访问。所有提供给SPTI公司的侵权材料的副本也将从SPTI网站上删除。</p><p><strong>C</strong><strong>．向指定代理人提供版权抗辩通知的步骤</strong></p><p>如果客观上证实您不实陈述某个产品或活动，但没有侵犯知识产权，您可能会承担相应的损害赔偿责任（包括成本和律师诉讼费）。因此，如果您不确定材料是否侵犯了知识产权，请在联系SPTI之前，与您的律师联系。。</p><p>如果会员认为他们的材料被删除或被禁止访问不属犯著作权，该会员可根据《数字千年版权法案》第512条（G）第（2）和第（3）款发送抗辩通知。向指定代理人发送的抗辩通知必须包含以下信息。</p><ol>	<li>您的签名（签名可以以电子形式即电子签名的方式提供）；</li>	<li>标识已删除或已被禁用的访问材料，及其在被删除或禁用之前出现的位置；</li>	<li>一份声明，声明指出根据伪证处罚法，您有充分的理由相信该材料被删除或禁用是材料错误或误认的结果。。</li>	<li>您的名字、地址、电话号码、电子邮箱以及一份同意联邦法院司法管辖的地址的声明，或者如果您的地址是在美国本土之外，但该地址应属于SPTI公司所在地的司法管辖区域内，这样您才能接收到那些根据17 U.S.C. 512中(c)(1)(C)的规定提供通知的个人或其代理人提供的服务进程信息。</li></ol><p>如果收到指定代理人的抗辩通知，SPTI可以发送抗辩通知副本，告知原申诉方，SPTI会取代移除的材料或在10个工作日内禁用它。除非版权或知识产权所有者对会员提交并寻求法院命令的行动，否则收到抗辩通知后，根据SPTI的自由裁量权，删除的材料可以在10至14个工作日内对它进行恢复访问。</p><p>请联系SPTI的指定代理人，通过电子邮件提交侵权和版权抗辩通知的声明<a href="mailto:legal@chiccablu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">legal@chicca-blu.com</span></a>&nbsp;（最佳方式），或联系以下地址：</p><p>指定代理接收侵权声明通知</p><p>有关版权法访问 <a href="http://www.copyright.gov/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.copyright.gov</span></a>以获取更多信息。有关专利法和商标法访问<a href="http://www.uspto.gov/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.uspto.gov</span></a>以获取更多信息。具体问题请咨询执照律师。</p>'),
