(8, 'TERMS', '<p>PLEASE READ THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS (&quot;AGREEMENT&quot; OR &quot;TERMS OF USE&quot;) CAREFULLY BEFORE USING <a href="http://www.chicca-blu.com"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chicca-blu.com</span></a> (THE &quot;SITE&quot;) OR ANY SERVICE OFFERED BY PERSONALIZED BEAUTY DISCOVERY, INC. (&quot;CHICCABLU,&quot; &quot;WE,&quot; OR &quot;US&quot;). UNLESS YOU ACCEPT THIS AGREEMENT YOU ARE NOT AUTHORIZED TO USE THE SITE OR ANY CHICCABLU SERVICE.&nbsp;<strong>BY VISITING, BROWSING, OR USING THE SITE OR ANY CHICCABLU SERVICE, YOU AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THIS AGREEMENT INCLUDING ANY ADDITIONAL TERMS, CONDITIONS, AND POLICIES INCORPORATED BY REFERENCE INTO IT.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Agreement applies to all Site visitors and users of the Site or CHICCABLU Services. If you don&#39;t agree with any term or condition in this Agreement, please don&#39;t use the Site or any CHICCABLU Service. If you have any questions, please refer to the Site&#39;s FAQs at&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chicca-blu.com/</span></a>. If you don&#39;t find your answer there, email us using this link:<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chicca-blu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>WELCOME TO CHICCABLU!</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">CHICCABLU operates an online beauty community on the Site and on social networking platforms controlled by CHICCABLU such as the CHICCABLU wechat page CHICCABLU Facebook<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;page, the CHICCABLU Instagram<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;and Pinterest<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;boards and the CHICCABLU Twitter<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;feed (collectively, the &quot;CHICCABLU Online Community&quot;). Our community is a place for you to express your unique beauty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">If you take the beauty quiz on our Site and register as an CHICCABLU member you become an &quot;chicster&quot;. There is no payment required to become a chiccster.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">You are not required to use social media at all to become a chiccster. We hope you share your unique beauty with other chiccster in the CHICCABLU Online Community, but you are not required to do so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">CHICCABLU offers its community members four beauty services: Glam Bag subscriptions, Points, CHICCABLU Offers and Brand offers (collectively, the &quot;CHICCABLU Services&quot;).</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Glam Bag Subscriptions</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Glam Bag Contents:</strong>&nbsp;Glam Bags typically contain 4 to 5 beauty items. The contents of each Glam Bag will vary from month to month. We customize your Glam Bag based on your CHICCABLU beauty profile, your product reviews and other feedback you choose to provide to us, but we make no guarantees that you will receive a particular product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Monthly Subscription:</strong>&nbsp;By purchasing a Monthly Subscription, you agree to an initial&nbsp;<strong>and recurring Monthly Subscription fee</strong>&nbsp;at the then-current Monthly Subscription rate, and you accept responsibility for all recurring charges prior to cancellation.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>AUTOMATIC MONTHLY RENEWAL TERMS: Once you subscribe and are off the waitlist, CHICCABLU will automatically process your Monthly Subscription fee in the next billing cycle. CHICCABLU will continue to automatically process your Monthly Subscription fee each month at the then-current Monthly Subscription rate without further notice to you or authorization from you, until you cancel your subscription. We explain how to cancel your Monthly Subscription below at the Section &quot;Cancellation Policy&quot;.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Annual Subscription:</strong>&nbsp;By purchasing an Annual Subscription, you agree to an initial pre-payment for one full year of service (after you are off the waitlist)&nbsp;<strong>and a recurring Annual Subscription renewal fee at the then-current Annual Subscription rate.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>AUTOMATIC ANNUAL RENEWAL TERMS: We bill your credit card for the Annual Subscription renewal fee in the first month of your next Annual Subscription.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:96.75pt">For example, let&#39;s say you purchased an Annual Subscription beginning in May 2015 and ending in April 2016. We will bill you for the second year (May 2016 to April 2017) in May 2016, unless you cancel your Annual Subscription before May 2016. You accept responsibility for all recurring charges prior to cancellation.&nbsp;<strong>Once you subscribe, CHICCABLU will automatically process your Annual Subscription fee at the then-current Annual Subscription rate without further notice to you or authorization from you until you cancel your subscription. We explain how to cancel your Annual Subscription below at the Section &quot;Cancellation Policy&quot;.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Waitlist:</strong>&nbsp;Our Glam Bags are in high demand so you may be placed on a waitlist when you first subscribe to the program. We try to convert members from the waitlist into active subscribers as quickly as possible, but the timing depends on a number of important factors including our ability to find and source the best and highest-quality brands and products that successfully meet the personal interests and needs identified in each new subscriber&#39;s beauty profile. We never want to compromise the caliber or experience of the Glam Bag program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Skip the Waitlist:</strong>&nbsp;At different points each month, we communicate through email and the CHICCABLU Facebook page special promotions to skip the waitlist. These promotions are intended to reward our biggest fans for helping to spread the word about CHICCABLU through social media. Skipping the waitlist is not required and is at each chiccster discretion.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Cancellation Policy for Monthly Subscription Renewals: You may cancel your Monthly Subscription at any time by logging into your account and following the cancellation procedures described there. If you need help with this email us using this link:&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099"><strong>help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</strong></span></a><strong>. If you are on the waitlist you cannot cancel by logging into your account, so please email us using the same link to cancel your waitlist Monthly Subscription. If you cancel your Monthly Subscription, the cancellation will take effect for your next Glam Bag monthly billing cycle. You will not be eligible for a refund for monthly subscription fees paid prior to the month the cancellation takes effect.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cancellation Policy for Annual Subscription Renewals: Annual Subscription fees are non-refundable. You may cancel your Annual Subscription renewal at any time after you were billed for the then-current year by logging into your account and following the cancellation procedures or by emailing us using this link: </strong><a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099"><strong>help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</strong></span></a><strong>.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">If you cancel your Glam Bag subscription you can re-subscribe any time, subject to the waitlist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>No Returns:</strong>&nbsp;You may not return any Glam Bag you receive. If you have concerns about the Glam Bag you have received please email CHICCABLUCare using this link: <a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>. We will work with you to address your concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Points</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">chiccsters residing in the United States or Canada may earn points redeemable on the Site (&quot;Points&quot;) for certain rewards products. You automatically enroll in the Points program when you subscribe to the Glam Bag or get on the waitlist to subscribe. You can find our Points program here:&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chiccablu.com/points</span></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Earning Points:</strong>&nbsp;To earn Points, you must be an active Glam Bag subscriber or on the waitlist. You can earn Points in a variety of ways. Check out the Site&#39;s Points tab for more information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Points Balance:</strong>&nbsp;You can check your Points balance at any time by signing into your CHICCABLU account and checking your Points tab on the Site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Redeeming Points:</strong>&nbsp;To redeem Points you must be an active Glam Bag subscriber. If you are on the waitlist you can&#39;t redeem Points. Points are redeemable towards rewards products (&quot;Rewards&quot;) solely on the Site as long as you have sufficient points for a Reward. Points can be used to redeem only one of each type of Reward. Redemption values will vary. Your Points have zero cash value, so you can&#39;t redeem them for cash or credit. To redeem your Points, simply go into your Activity Log and view the Rewards available at that time. If you see something you like and you have earned the required number of Points, click the button that says &quot;REDEEM THIS&quot;. When you click this button, your Points will be used, and the Reward you have chosen will be shipped in your next Glam Bag shipping cycle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Expiration of Points:</strong>&nbsp;Points expire one year from the date they were first earned even if you&#39;re an active Glam Bag subscriber or on the waitlist. If you don&#39;t redeem your Points within this time frame, you will automatically forfeit them. Your Points Activity shows you the dates on which you earned your Points.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Limited Availability of Rewards:</strong>&nbsp;Rewards are available only while supplies last and quantities may be limited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>No Returns:</strong>&nbsp;You may not return any Reward you receive by redeeming Points. Since Points have no cash value, we will not issue any cash or credit for them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Effect of Glam Bag Subscription Cancellation:</strong>&nbsp;If you cancel your Glam Bag subscription, we will save your Points until their expiration date one year from the date they were first earned. If you re-subscribe within that time period, your Points will be right there waiting for you, though they will continue to expire one year from the date they were first earned (see &quot;Expiration of Points&quot; Section above). If you cancel your Glam Bag subscription before we are able to ship you your Reward, then we will instead refund your Points to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Questions:</strong>&nbsp;If you have any questions about the Points program, please visit us at&nbsp;help www.chicca-blu.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>CHICCABLU Offers</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">CHICCABLU uncovers amazing beauty finds from brands we love and offers them for purchase on the Site to ipsters residing in the United States. You can find CHICCABLU Offers here:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.chicca-blu.com/offers"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chicca-blu.com/offers</span></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>How to purchase an CHICCABLU Offer:</strong>&nbsp;Go to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.chicca-blu.com/offers"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.chicca-blu.com/offers</span></a>&nbsp;to find CHICCABLU Offers. We also post CHICCABLU Offers on our social media platforms on a regular basis, so keep an eye out for great products at great prices! You do not need to be an ipster to purchase CHICCABLU Offers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Limited Availability:</strong>&nbsp;CHICCABLU Offers are available for purchase only during the Offer period and only while supplies last, on a first-come, first-served basis. Quantities will be very limited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Receiving Your CHICCABLU Offer:</strong>&nbsp;If you purchase a particular CHICCABLU Offer, you will receive an email from CHICCABLU confirming all of the details of your order (&quot;Confirmation Email&quot;). Orders you don&#39;t cancel (see &quot;Cancellation of CHICCABLU Offer&quot; Section below) will be shipped to the address on file in your CHICCABLU account. We ship by standard ground shipping. Certain CHICCABLU Offers may qualify for discounted or free shipping; all such CHICCABLU Offers will be clearly labeled.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Cancellation of CHICCABLU Offer:</strong>&nbsp;You may cancel your CHICCABLU Offer order after receiving the Confirmation Email, but only if we have not shipped the Offer to you yet. You must write to us using this link&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>&nbsp;to cancel your CHICCABLU Offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Returns:</strong>&nbsp;If you are not entirely happy with your CHICCABLU Offer, you may return it to CHICCABLU within 30 days of your purchase. All returned CHICCABLU Offers must be unused, in their original packaging and in new and sellable condition. CHICCABLU will refund the purchase price back to the credit card you used, less a USD$5.00 restocking fee. Refunds may take up to ten business days to process. Return shipping and handling are free when you contact CHICCABLUCare and use the return label that we provide. We will not refund original shipping charges unless an error on our part caused the return. Because of the limited quantities of CHICCABLU Offers, there will be no exchanges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Questions:</strong>&nbsp;If you have any questions about CHICCABLU Offers, please see our FAQs at:&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.www.chicca-blu.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Giveaways</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt"><strong>Consumer Disclosure</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">From time to time CHICCABLU runs contests for ipsters (our registered CHICCABLU members), based on a combination of skill and chance, to win beauty products. We call these contests &quot;CHICCABLU Giveaways&quot; and &quot;Guru Giveaways&quot; (together &quot;Giveaways&quot;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">You can find out about Giveaways on the Site. at&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">gurugiveaways.com</span></a>, or on CHICCABLU&#39;s social media platforms. For example, we may announce a contest on our YouTube channel or through our Twitter feed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Your participation in any Giveaway will be subject to and governed by the official rules set forth below and, if applicable, the rules on the Site page for Giveaways.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Sometimes social media platforms such as YouTube have their own contest rules too, which are in addition to the rules listed below. For example, YouTube requires all contest entrants to follow the YouTube Community Rules, such as not posting violent videos. You can read about these additional rules, which CHICCABLU does not control, on each social media platform&#39;s site. For example, here is a link to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>YouTube&#39;s Terms of Service:<span style="color:#ff0099">&nbsp;</span><a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">youtube.com/t/terms</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:96.75pt">and</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>YouTube&#39;s Community Guidelines:&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">youtube.com/t/community_guidelines</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:60.75pt">Here are the CHICCABLU Giveaway contest official rules:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND IS NECESSARY TO WIN THIS CONTEST.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>The contest is open to legal residents of the United States and Canada.</li>\r\n	<li>To enter the contest you must be 18 years or older, or the age of majority in your state of residence if the age of majority is greater than 18.</li>\r\n	<li>Odds of winning are based on the number of prizes awarded in each Giveaway out of notices distributed to all followers of our CHICCABLU Online Community.</li>\r\n	<li>You must enter the contest within a specific timeframe. The beginning and end of the contest will be stated in the Giveaway notice.</li>\r\n	<li>We announce the winners of our CHICCABLU Giveaways by posting each winner&#39;s social media name or handle on the platform where we originally promoted that CHICCABLU Giveaway. We make this announcement within 15 days of the end of the CHICCABLU Giveaway.</li>\r\n	<li>If your social media name or handle appears in our winners announcement, then you must contact CHICCABLUCare at <a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">help.chiccablu.com/customer/portal/emails/new</span></a>&nbsp;within 15 days to claim your prize and provide a shipping address for your prize.</li>\r\n	<li>When we run CHICCABLU Giveaways on social media platforms, please note that the promotion is in no way sponsored, associated or endorsed by the social media platforms. For example,&nbsp;<em>CHICCABLU Giveaways we post on Wechat Facebook, YouTube or Instagram are in no way sponsored, associated or endorsed by Facebook, YouTube or Instagram</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Participants in our Guru Giveaways find out if they have won immediately after entering. The results appear on the&nbsp;<a href="http://tbsdemo.in/chiccablu/terms" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">gurugiveaways.com</span></a>&nbsp;page.</li>\r\n	<li>We send prizes by ground shipping to addresses in the United States or Canada. We cannot ship prizes to post office box addresses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>PRODUCT MANUFACTURE AND INGREDIENTS</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">We don&#39;t manufacture any of the beauty products we send to you. Glam Bag items and the products distributed with Offers, Points and Giveaways are manufactured by their respective brands. You should read and strictly follow all product labels, packaging inserts and instructions, and manufacturer directions and warnings before using any product. We review the ingredients in each beauty product we distribute to confirm the ingredients comply with industry standards. It is your responsibility to review the ingredients as well, to avoid allergic reactions or other side effects personal to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">U.S. residents who want to report a concern regarding any cosmetic product obtained from any source can contact the U.S. Food and Drug Administration at <a href="http://www.fda.gov/Cosmetics/ComplianceEnforcement/AdverseEventReporting/default.htm" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">http://www.fda.gov/Cosmetics/ComplianceEnforcement/AdverseEventReporting/default.htm</span></a>. Canadian residents can complete a Consumer Product Incident Report Form at <a href="http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ff0099">www.hc-sc.gc.ca</span></a>. Chinese residents can report a concern regarding cosmetic product obtained from any source can contact the China Food and Drug Administration. http://www.sda.gov.cn/WS01/CL0001/</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Eligibility to Use the Site and CHICCABLU Services</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>General:</strong>&nbsp;You may access the Site from anywhere in the world without incurring any fees or becoming an ipster. However, you will be required to join CHICCABLU and be a legal resident of the United States or Canada to use certain Site features and CHICCABLU Services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>Residency:</strong>&nbsp;The Site is available to anyone in the world, the CHICCABLU Services are available to anyone in the world. The Glam Bag subscription service, the Points program and Giveaways are available to anyone in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>Fees:</strong>&nbsp;It&#39;s free to use the Site, earn Points and win Giveaways, but the Glam Bag and CHICCABLU Offers services each require that you pay a fee.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>Age:</strong>&nbsp;You are not authorized to access or use the Site or any CHICCABLU Service if you are under 13 years old. Individuals under 18 years old must at all times use the Site and CHICCABLU Services only in conjunction with and under the supervision of a parent, or the supervision of a legal guardian who is at least 18 years old. In all cases, that parent or legal guardian is the Site user (or Site member or Glam Bag subscriber, if applicable) and will be responsible for any and all use of the Site and CHICCABLU Services by the individual under 18.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>Compliance:</strong>&nbsp;To be eligible to use the Site and CHICCABLU Services, you must comply with all local laws regarding online conduct and acceptable content and agree to pay all applicable taxes. Use of the Site is void where prohibited by law. You must also comply with these Terms of Use, the CHICCABLU policy documents listed below (if applicable to your use of the Site or CHICCABLU Services), and all other operating rules, policies, and procedures that CHICCABLU may publish from time to time on the Site, each of which is incorporated herein by reference and each of which CHICCABLU may update from time to time without notice to you:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="list-style-type:circle">\r\n	<li>CHICCABLU Privacy Policy</li>\r\n	<li>CHICCABLU Cookie and Tracking Policy</li>\r\n	<li>CHICCABLU Copyright and Intellectual Property Policy</li>\r\n	<li>CHICCABLU Community Guidelines</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt">Certain CHICCABLU Services may be subject to additional terms and conditions that CHICCABLU may post on the Site from time to time. To be eligible for such services, you must comply with those additional terms and conditions, which are incorporated by reference into this Agreement. See Section 5 below for more information regarding modifications to these Terms of Use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.75pt"><strong>CHICCABLU&#39;s Right to Revoke, Suspend, or Restrict Eligibility:</strong>&nbsp;CHICCABLU reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to cancel unconfirmed or inactive accounts. CHICCABLU may, in its sole discretion, for any reason, at any time, revoke, suspend, or restrict your access to the Site or any CHICCABLU Service. If CHICCABLU bans you from the Site or any CHICCABLU Service, you may not return to the Site or use that CHICCABLU Service for any reason or in any manner including with a new username or identity. In the event that you return, or attempt to return, to the Site or use the CHIC