(5, 'BLENDCLEANSER', 'FANTASTIC FOUR SOAP AND 3D BLEND CLEANSER', 'QQæˆªå›¾20160309172518-1457515730-88590.png', 500, 50, 0, '<p>The 3D Blenders medium and small size with soap, is designed with a slightly more dense texture than other blenders that not only fits the contours of the face but gives the sponge a lengthier life cycle. Ergonomically shaped, 100% latex-free and easy-to-use, these mini miracles make foundation application, contouring, and highlighting a snap! They can be used wet or dry and are completely reusable! Simply wash with soap and water and let dry.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Re-usable</li>\r\n	<li>Can be used wet or dry</li>\r\n	<li>Great for contouring and highlighting</li>\r\n	<li>Small size 3D blend for tight corner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>0.10 oz</p>\r\n', 'hydrophilic polyurethane foam', '2016-03-09 09:28:50', 'BLENDCLEANSER', '神奇的四色皂以及3D混合洗面奶', '<p>这款3D大小混合面皂相对于其他普通面皂质地更为致密，在设计在采用了符合面部线条的流线型设计，符合人体工程力学的设计不但更易于清洁，同时也延长了海绵的使用寿命，100%无乳胶添加，易于使用。这些小小的改进使得脸部清洁更加彻底，轮廓更为突显，肤色更加靓丽。面皂可干湿两用并可重复使用，只需简单直接用皂清洁脸部或加水使用。</p><ul>	<li>可重复使用</li>	<li>干湿两用</li>	<li>重塑线条和提亮肤色效果明显</li>	<li>小尺寸3D面皂用于死区清洁</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>2.83克</p>', '<p><span style="color:black; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">亲水性聚氨酯泡沫</span></p>'),
(6, 'ALAOUOOUO', 'PROFESSIONAL EYESHADOW MAKUP', 'QQæˆªå›¾20160309173044-1457515950-64701.png', 600, 50, 0, '<p>Just in time for the spring comes Alaouoouo Quad Eye shadow in Silver and Purple hues! From night time parties to cool daytime events, complete your look with these festive shimmery shades.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Four shimmery shades</li>\r\n	<li>Rich pigmentation</li>\r\n	<li>Long-lasting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>0.12 oz</p>\r\n', 'talc, dimethicone, mica, ethlyhexyl palmitate, magnesium stearate, silica, mineral oil, caprylic/capric triglyceride, polybutene, phenoxyethanol, ethlyhexylglycerin [may contain (+/-) titanium dioxide, red iron oxide, yellow iron oxide, black iron oxide]', '2016-03-09 09:32:30', 'ALAOUOOUO', '微光闪耀眼影套盒', '<p>Alaouooue Quad 银色和紫色色调眼影套盒帮你塑造最美的春季妆容，从晚妆到日妆，这款眼影能够满足你的所有日常妆容需求。</p><ul>	<li>华丽闪烁的四色色调</li>	<li>丰富的色素沉着</li>	<li>持久力强</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>3.4克</p>', '<p>滑石，二甲基硅氧烷，云母，棕榈酸乙基己酯，硬脂酸镁，二氧化硅，矿物油，辛酸/癸酸甘油三酯，聚丁烯，苯氧基乙醇，乙基己基甘油[可能含有二氧化钛，氧化铁红，黄色氧化铁，黑色氧化铁</p>'),
(7, 'BAISIDAI', 'Fashion Eye Lashes', 'QQæˆªå›¾20160309173402-1457516122-2380.png', 500, 50, 0, '<p>Baisidai #1340 Lashes are perfect for enhancing your eyes for an everyday look. They create the look of full, beautiful lashes. Lightweight and reusable, these lashes are permanently curled, waterproof, comfortable to wear and easy to apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Natural looking</li>\r\n	<li>Enhances eyes</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to apply</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>.3 oz</p>\r\n', '100% sterilized natural hair', '2016-03-09 09:35:22', 'BAISIDAI', '时尚假睫毛', '<p>Baisidai 1340 号睫毛自然浓密，拥有它就拥有了你梦寐以求的浓眉大眼，永久卷曲，无重感，可重复使用，防水，操作简单，带上后几乎感受不到它的存在。</p><ul>	<li>简约自然</li>	<li>提亮双眼</li>	<li>使用拿捏方便</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong> 8.5克</p>', '<p><span style="font-family:roboto; font-size:12pt">100% </span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif; font-size:12pt">无菌自然毛发</span></p>'),
(8, 'PENS', 'Nail Polish', 'QQæˆªå›¾20160309173619-1457516297-54870.png', 600, 50, 0, '<p>Formulated with love in the USA and EU, Pens is always vegan and cruelty-free. If you&rsquo;re looking to minimize the toxic content you&rsquo;re exposed to, and you believe you can be beautiful without being cruel, Pens is the indie nail polish brand for you. This coral shade will let everyone know that you really are a big deal!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-toxic</li>\r\n	<li>Long-wear</li>\r\n	<li>Cruelty-free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>.57 oz</p>\r\n', 'butyl acetate, ethyl acetate, nitrocellulose, acetyl tributyl citrate, adipic acid/ neopentyl glycol/ trimellitic anhydride copolymer, isopropyl alcohol, stearalkonium bentonite, acrylates copolymer, styrene/ acrylates, copolymer, may contain: ci 77891, ci 19140, ci 15850, ci 15850, ci 15880, ci 77491,_ci 77499, ci 77510, ci 77163 polyethylene terephthalate, aluminium powder, mica, dibenzoate', '2016-03-09 09:38:17', 'PENS', '指甲油', '<p>Pens始终遵循美国和欧盟提倡的在化妆品中使用植物原料不做伤害动物性行为。如果你正在寻找绿色纯天然无毒化妆品并且坚信对美的追求不应凌驾于残酷性行为之上，Pens会是你的首选。此款香水指甲油会使每个人认为你真的很重要。</p><ul>	<li>无有害性物质</li>	<li>持久不掉色</li>	<li>未采用动物原料</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong> 16.15克</p>', '<p>乙酸丁酯，乙酸乙酯，硝化纤维素，乙酰柠檬酸三丁酯，己二酸/新戊二醇/偏苯三酸酐共聚物，异丙醇，硬脂膨润土，丙烯酸酯共聚物，苯乙烯/丙烯酸酯，共聚物，可能含有：CI77891，CI19140，CI15850，CI15850，CI15880，CI77491，_CI77499，CI77510，CI77163聚乙烯对苯二甲酸酯，铝粉，云母，二苯甲酸</p>'),
(9, 'NYX', 'BUTTER LIPSTICK', 'QQæˆªå›¾20160309173948-1457516447-28226.png', 700, 50, 0, '<p>&nbsp;Hydrate your lips with this moisturizing combination of full coverage lipstick and creamy chapstick in one! Not only will you be rocking a gorgeous pout, this lipstick is designed to keep your lips feeling smooth and moisturized all day long. Plus, it smells &amp; feels like butter.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hydrating</li>\r\n	<li>Full coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Creamy satin finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>.3 oz</p>\r\n', 'candelilla wax, bees wax, carnauba wax, capric/caprylic triglyceride, tridecyl trimellitate, olive oil, 2-ethyihexyl palmitate, sunchemical, tocopherol, propylparaben. may contain: red6 (c115850), red7 (c115850:1), red27 (c116035:1), yellow5 (c119140:1), titanium dioxide (c177891), iron oxide black (c177499), blue1 (c142090:2), iron oxide yellow (c177492)', '2016-03-09 09:40:47', 'NYX', '黄油口红', '<p>唇膏和口红二合一带给你全天候滋润水嫩的双唇。此款口红外观是丝绒感，一触丝滑，含有黄油保温精华，轻盈顺滑不干燥，涂抹之后令双唇倍感亮泽饱满。此外，闻起来和使用时有黄油的香味。</p><ul>	<li>滋润</li>	<li>显色</li>	<li>奶油嗅感及触感</li></ul><p><strong>重量：</strong>8.5克</p>', '<p><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">烛树蜡，蜂蜡，巴西棕榈蜡，癸酸</span><span style="font-family:roboto">/</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">辛酸甘油三酯，十三烷基偏苯三酸酯，橄榄油，棕榈酸辛酯，</span><span style="font-family:roboto">sunchemical</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">，生育酚，对羟基苯甲酸丙酯。可以含有：红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">6</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c115850</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">7</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c115850</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），红</span><span style="font-family:roboto">27</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c116035</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），黄</span><span style="font-family:roboto">5</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c119140</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），二氧化钛（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177891</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），氧化铁黑（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177499</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），蓝</span><span style="font-family:roboto">1</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">色淀（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c142090</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">：</span><span style="font-family:roboto">2</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">），铁氧化铁黄（</span><span style="font-family:roboto">c177492</span><span style="font-family:arial unicode ms,sans-serif">）</span><span style="font-family:roboto">...)</span></p>'),
(10, 'GLAMOUR DOLLS', 'DOUBLE BAKED FACE BLUSH', 'æœªæ ‡é¢˜-2-1457593977-64985.jpg', 800, 50, 0, '<p>A fresh blush of brush-on sunshine without the UV damage. Sheer and buildable highlighter powder complements every skin tone, adds just enough of a natural summery glow and a glimpse of shimmer. Great when you&rsquo;re feeling a bit tired, or just longing for the beach!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEIGHT: </strong>0.12 oz</p>\r\n', 'talc, mica, magnesium stearate, stearic acid, ethylhexyl palmitate, paraffinum liquidum, polybutene, microcrystalline wax, bees wax, dimethicone may contain (+/-): red iron oxide ci 77491, titaninium dioxide ci 77891, black iron oxide ci 77499, brown iron oxide ci 77491/92/99, red no 6 ba ci 15850', '2016-03-09 09:42:37', 'GLAMOUR DOLLS ', '双色腮红', '<p>这款清新自然色彩柔和的腮红让你远离紫外线的伤害。荧光粉有助力于提亮肤色，自然通透感与鲜活粉嫩结合得恰到好处。在你感到一丝丝疲惫或者想要出发去海滩的时候使用能够使你马上展现出粉嫩好气色。</p><p><strong>重量：</strong>3.4克</p>', '<p>滑石，云母，硬脂酸镁，硬脂酸，乙基己基棕榈酸酯，石蜡油，聚丁烯，微晶蜡，蜂蜡，聚二甲基硅氧烷</p><p>可能含有（+/-）：氧化铁红CI77491，二氧化钛CI77891，氧化铁黑CI77499，氧化铁棕CI77491/92/99，红6号巴茨15850</p>');
